95100000-null-.name: Items Worth Paying Attention To
95100000-null-.desc: Some outfits obtained from the $item:20301206$ contain hidden quests! Pay attention to the outfit icons and tooltips to find them!

95100001-null-.name: Items Worth Paying Attention To
95100001-null-.desc: Some outfits grant special rewards when you equip the full set, so pay attention when you see an explanation mark on an outfit's icon!

10001001-null-.name: The Start of a Journey
10001001-null-.desc: I heard from $npc:11000062$ that the upcoming levee for the Empress will be open to the public. It's going to be a once in a lifetime opportunity you won't want to miss. Should I attend as well?
10001001-null-.manual: Talk to $npc:11000016$ in $map:63000002$ to board a ship headed towards Lith Harbor

10001002-null-.name: The Empress' Levee
10001002-null-.desc:
It was nice seeing $npc:11000080$ the island boy again in $map:02000062$. You'll probably find even more familiar faces in $map:02000001$.
The Royal Road that connects $map:02000062$ and $map:02000001$ should make the journey quick and easy.
But first, find a path that connects $map:02000062$ to $map:02000114$.
10001002-null-.manual: Go to $map:02000001$, the location where the levee will be held

10001010-null-.name: Porters in Danger
10001010-null-.desc: The porters that carried the goods in preparation for the levee came to $map:02000116$ despite the dangers that awaited. It seems that some particularly thorny vines may have trapped some of them. Try and save any porters you come across.
10001010-null-.manual: Rescue the porters stuck inside the vines in $map:02000116$

10001011-null-.name: Relaying the Message
10001011-null-.desc:
$npc:11000129$ says that there is a group that went on ahead into $map:02000117$. I was asked to meet them to relay the tale of the porters that have fallen into trouble, and ask them to wait until everyone has arrived.
Let's head on over to $map:02000117$ to look for another royal porter.

10001050-null-.name: A Boy's Curiosity
10001050-null-.desc: Although she nags every now and then, $npc:11000107$ is a kind sister that is simply worried for $npc:11000114$. But where could $npc:11000114$ have gone? Could he really have gone to Royal Road?

10001070-null-.name: A Stinging Revolt
10001070-null-.desc:
The honey bees that have worked hard to gather all this honey are furious ever since $npc:22000022$ stole their honey.
You should give $npc:22000022$'s honey pot to the honey bees that have lost their food.
Look for a pot of honey below a stone roof in $map:02000117$, where $npc:22000022$ appears.
10001070-null-.manual: Recover the pot of honey in $map:02000117$

10001110-null-.name: Pincerific Choice
10001110-null-.desc:
It seems as though $npc:11000098$ really likes $npc:11000151$.
You can get $item:30000011$ by catching $npc:21000059$ right? Well then, you better stretch and get warmed up! You don't want to pull a muscle!
Go to $map:63000002$ and catch $npc:21000059$ to gather $item:30000011$.

10001111-null-.name: Everything for Her
10001111-null-.desc:
Is $npc:11000151$ simply horrible at expressing her feelings, or is she just always this blunt?
Is it possible that $npc:11000151$'s boyfriend had enough of her abrasive attitude and decided not to return from $map:63000002$?
10001111-null-.complete: Go to $map:63000002$ after checking the location by pressing the M key

10001121-null-.name: Unusual Circumstances
10001121-null-.desc:
Poor $npc:11000118$…
She needs some assistance after injuring her hand. Someone needs to help her harvest the clams that hold pearls in $map:63000002$!
Start searching for $item:30000008$!

10001130-null-.name: O Turtle! My Turtle!
10001130-null-.desc:
$npc:11000053$ made a request to bring $item:20000013$, which is located at Turtle Hill where $npc:22300149$ appears.
It's not going to be easy...but nothing worthwhile ever is, right?

10001140-null-.name: Leaving Lith Harbor
10001140-null-.desc:
Are there not enough ships because so many people are trying to go to $map:02000062$? 
If that's the case, it'll probably be best to go to $map:63000002$ port and speak with $npc:11000016$ personally to see if a ship is available.

10001330-null-.name: The Fates That Bind Us
10001330-null-.desc:
I met $npc:11000110$ again in Victoria Island and he made another request. I don't hesitate to help those who I've only met once, so there's no reason why I can't help someone I've known since Maple Island.
Let's defeat the monsters in the grass underneath the $map:02000114$ bridge, and find item:30000054$ that $npc:11000110$ lost.
10001330-null-.manual: Defeat the monsters in $map:02000114$ and recover $item:30000054$

10001340-null-.name: An Unexpected Event
10001340-null-.desc:
The Royal Guard are also confused by the sudden earthquake.
They're quickly trying to find out what caused the earthquake... Maybe I can lend a hand?
I'll carry the equipment box that lies near $npc:11000157$ and move it below the stairs.
10001340-null-.manual: Move the equipment box that lies near $npc:11000157$ down the stairs

10001350-null-.name: Strong Eats
10001350-null-.desc:
$map:02000001$'s safety is at jeopardy if hunger also becomes a factor in these intense battles.
Defeat the monsters in $map:02000118$ and bring back the $item:20000014$ that the monsters have taken.
10001350-null-.manual: Bring back the $item:20000014$ that the $map:02000118$ monsters have taken

10001690-null-.name: QUESTDESCRIPTION_10001690_NAME
10001690-null-.desc:
$npc:11000374$, whom I met in $map:02000117$, told me of a great moneymaking venture that involves getting $item:30000112$ and then bringing it to $npc:11000546$.
Let's go hunt $npc:21000062$, gather $item:30000112$, and hand them over to $npc:11000546$.

10001700-null-.name: Secret of the Mushroom
10001700-null-.desc:
$npc:11000375$, whom I met in $map:02000117$, told me that he would pay well for $item:20000058$, a rare herb found only in the most pristine of areas.
The path may be narrow and the monsters tough...but I think it's worth a shot, since $npc:11000375$ will most likely pay very well.
Let's go to $map:02000117$ and collect $item:20000058$.

60001150-null-.name: The Royal Rumble
60001150-null-.desc: $npcName:11004285$, queen of the Pink Beans, has descended upon Maple World! This mysterious monarch is hosting the Queen Bean Rumble, a massive tournament with a huge cash prize. Speak with $npc:11004287$ in $map:83000001$ for details. You can get there by pressing the 'Queen Bean Rumble' dungeon's 'Lobby' button in the Challenge Map.

60001160-null-.name: For the Queen's Joy!
60001160-null-.desc: You asked $npcName:11004287$ about $npcName:11004285$, which naturally prompted him to call you a dirty peasant who grew up in a cave. Still, this queen of beans is hosting the Queen Bean Rumble, which comes with a sizable reward.

10001082-null-.name: 손녀를 위해서라면
10001082-null-.desc:
$npc:11000188$$pp:를,을$ 향한 $npc:11000187$의 사랑과 관심이 그대로 전해진다.
$npc:11000188$$pp:가,이$ 어서 몸을 회복할 수 있도록 나도 도와야겠다. $map:02000059$$pp2:로,으로$ 가자.

10001082-null-NA.name: A Grandmother's Love
10001082-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000187$ is deeply worried for the health of her granddaughter $npcName:11000188$, and has asked you to get medicine from an herbalist in $map:02000059$.

10001083-null-.name: 방랑 약초꾼
10001083-null-.desc:
$npc:11000190$$pp:는,은$ 참 무심한 남편인 것 같다.
일단, $npc:11000192$$pp:를,을$ 찾아가서 $npcName:11000190$의 행방을 알아보자.

10001083-null-NA.name: That Man of Mine
10001083-null-NA.desc: It seems that $npcName:11000190$ wandered off days ago without any consideration for his wife and children, and hasn't been back since. You should talk see if $npcName:11000192$ the $npcTitle:11000192$ knows where $npcName:11000190$ went.

10001084-null-.name: 약초꾼에게 필요한 건?
10001084-null-.desc:
간단히 구할 수 있을 줄 알았는데…  $npc:11000190$$pp:를,을$ 만나기가 이리 어려울 줄이야… 
$npc:11000187$에게 이미 약초를 구해다 주겠다고 약속을 했으니 이제 와서 포기할 수도 없다.
일단, $item:30000026$$pp:를,을$ 들고 $map:02000059$의 $npc:11000192$의 집 바로 아래에 있다고 하는 $map:02000082$$pp2:로,으로$ 가서 $npc:11000190$$pp:를,을$ 찾아보자.

10001084-null-NA.name: O Husband, Where Art Thou?
10001084-null-NA.desc:
What started as a simple trip to pick up medicine has turned into a missing persons case, and now two families are counting on you to find $npcName:11000190$.

Take $npcName:11000190$'s $item:30000026$ and search for him in the $map:02000082$, which is located right below $npcName:11000192$'s house in $map:02000059$.

10001085-null-.name: 비법서를 찾아서
10001085-null-.desc:
$npc:11000190$$pp:는,은$ 건망증이 심한 것 같다.
그가 부지런히 비법서를 만들어 놓은 것도 다 이 건망증 때문에 생긴 버릇이겠지…?
아무튼 $map:02000059$에 있는 $map:02000151$에서 약초 비법서를 찾아보자.
10001085-null-.complete: $map:02000059$에 있는 약초꾼의 집에서 약초 비법서 찾기

10001085-null-NA.name: A Recipe for Disasters
10001085-null-NA.desc:
Being a forgetful man, $npc:11000190$ carefully documents all his notes on herbs and plants in a guide book. If you can find the book, you should be able to discern how to help $npcName:11000188$.

Go to $map:02000151$ in $map:02000059$ and look for the herb guide.
10001085-null-NA.complete: Find the herb guide in the herbalist's house in $map:02000059$

10001086-null-.name: 황금 사과의 비밀
10001086-null-.desc:
$npc:11000190$의 비법서에는 $item:20000044$$pp:가,이$ 몸을 따뜻하게 해 주는 효능이 있다고 적혀 있다.
$map:02000059$에서 황금 사과나무를 찾아보자.

10001086-null-NA.name: Eat Fruits and Leaves
10001086-null-NA.desc:
According to $npc:11000190$'s herb guide, a $item:20000044$ just might help restore $npcName:11000188$'s health.

Go shake some $item:20000044$ trees in $map:02000059$!

10001090-null-.name: 나무장작 쟁탈전
10001090-null-.desc:
$npc:11000203$$pp:는,은$ 몬스터들이 나무 장작을 훔쳐가는 바람에 화가 많이 난 것 같다.
$map:02000059$에서 $map:02000054$$pp2:로,으로$ 가는 길에 움푹 패인 땅에 쌓여 있는 장작더미를 $npc:11000203$ 앞으로 옮겨주자.

10001090-null-NA.name: Get Your Hands Off My Wood
10001090-null-NA.desc:
$npcName:11000203$ the $npcTitle:11000203$ is furious about monsters making off with his firewood.

You should grab any firewood you find on the path to $map:02000054$ and bring it back to him.
10001090-null-NA.manual: Place $npcName:11000203$'s liberated firewood in front of him

10001100-null-.name: 가장의 의무
10001100-null-.desc:
$npc:11000190$$pp:는,은$ $map:02000082$에서 계속 버섯을 캐고 있을 모양이다. 
때가 되면 그도 집으로 돌아가겠지… 
나가는 길에 $npcName:11000190$$pp:를,을$ 위해 $map:02000082$의 불 꺼진 양초를 다시 켜주고, $map:02000059$에서 $npc:11000191$$pp:를,을$ 만나보자.

10001100-null-NA.name: A Father's Duty
10001100-null-NA.desc:
It looks like $npcName:11000190$ has decided to stay in $map:02000082$ and harvest more mushrooms. 

He's asked you to deliver a bag-full to $npc:11000191$ in $map:02000059$, and re-light some candles on your way out.

10001151-null-.name: Iron Transformation
10001151-null-.desc:
$npc:11000181$ of $map:02000084$ mistakenly assigned you work, thinking you were a worker who had just recently started.
The assignment was to heat up the blast furnace to make an iron mold... Having this kind of experience can only help, right?
Go to $map:02000084$ and gather the $item:30000120$ needed to make the $item:30000121$ with the blast furnace.
10001151-null-.manual: Make $item:30000121$ at the blast furnace in $map:02000084$

10001230-null-.name: Quite a Quandary
10001230-null-.desc:
$map:02000100$'s $npc:11000065$ seems to be stuck in a predicament regarding the conflict between Goldus Pharmaceutical and the residents.
What a sticky situation...
Try to find out some more information and meet with $npc:11000216$, who is participating in the demonstration in front of $map:02000154$.

10001231-null-.name: Transparency Is a Virtue
10001231-null-.desc:
It seems the demonstration won't end until full transparency is achieved, and the whole truth is revealed.
$npc:11000216$ begged you to gather any sort of evidence that could help expose the truth.
Begin your investigation with aplomb by heading over to $map:02000134$.

10001232-null-.name: An Inconvenient Truth
10001232-null-.desc:
$map:02000134$'s $npc:11000124$ told you how to procure the material that may serve as evidence of how products from Goldus Pharmaceutical brought upon negative side effects.
Make your way to $map:02000159$ connected to $map:02000134$, and activate both the drug mixing and data collecting devices to find $item:30000049$ and $item:20000048$.

10001240-null-.name: Lifetime Duty
10001240-null-.desc:
The new drug $npc:11000124$ risked life and limb to create...
Providing some assistance could be the perfect opportunity to ask him to help uncover the truth behind the drug's side effects.
Head on over to $map:02000134$ to defeat all the monsters that have invaded, and look for $npc:11000124$'s $item:20000050$.

10001250-null-.name: 사라진 고양이
10001250-null-.desc:
$npc:11000217$의 주인님이 애지중지하는 고양이 $npc:11000049$$pp:가,이$ 낭떠러지 벽 틈에 갇혀서 빠져 나오지 못하고 있다.
벽타기나 풍선날기 스킬로 낭떠러지 벽 틈으로 들어가서 $npc:11000049$$pp:를,을$ 구하자.

10001250-null-NA.name: The Cat in the Cliff
10001250-null-NA.desc:
$npcName:11000217$'s boss's cat $npc:11000049$ is stuck on the side of a cliff and in need of rescue.

Defy the law of gravity by way of wall-climbing or flying mount, and rescue $npc:11000049$.
10001250-null-NA.manual: Rescue $npc:11000049$ from the side of the cliff in $map:02000137$

10001290-null-.name: 위험한 연구소
10001290-null-.desc:
$map:02000145$$pp:는,은$ 갑자기 들이닥친 몬스터들의 행패로 아수라장이었다. 곳곳에 몬스터의 공격을 받고 쓰러진 연구원들 사이에서 겨우 정신을 차리고 있던 $npc:11000125$$pp:는,은$ 몬스터들이 실험 중이던 $item:20000049$$pp:를,을$ 가지고 갔다며, 연구 센터 밖으로 $item:20000049$$pp:가,이$ 유출되기 전에 몬스터들을 처치하고 이를 되찾아달라고 부탁했다.
연구소 밖으로 유출되면 생태계에 대 혼란을 야기할 수도 있는 $item:20000049$! 
$map:02000145$$pp:를,을$ 습격한 몬스터들을 처치하고 녀석들이 가지고 간 $item:20000049$$pp:를,을$ 되찾아 유출을 막도록 하자!

10001290-null-NA.name: Containment Breach
10001290-null-NA.desc:
$map:02000145$ was thrust into chaos by an invasion of monsters, resulting in the injury of numerous researchers. But worse, they escaped with highly experimental $itemPlural:20000049$ that could wreak havoc on the environment should they escape the lab.

$npc:11000125$ has tasked you with defeating the monsters and retrieving the samples before it's too late.

10001300-null-.name: 사랑은 너무 어려워
10001300-null-.desc:
알 수 없는 이유로 갑자기 토라진 여자친구를 달래기 위해 $npc:11000223$$pp:는,은$ 여자친구가 풀밭에 던져버린 $item:30000046$$pp:를,을$ 찾고 있다.
$npc:11000223$의 사랑을 위해 $map:02000135$ 풀밭을 뒤져서 $item:30000046$$pp:를,을$ 찾아주자.

10001300-null-NA.name: Love Hurts
10001300-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000223$'s girlfriend got upset and threw her $item:30000046$ away. Before he can patch things up with her, he needs your help to recover it.

Search $map:02000135$ for the missing $item:30000046$.
10001300-null-NA.manual: Search the field in $map:02000135$ for the $item:30000046$

10001301-null-.name: 여자의 언어
10001301-null-.desc:
$npc:11000223$의 여자친구가 화가 난 진짜 이유가 뭘까?
$map:02000135$ 케이블카를 타고 올라가서 레스토랑에 있는 $npc:11000224$$pp:를,을$ 만나서 물어보자.

10001301-null-NA.name: Reasonable Expectations
10001301-null-NA.desc: Why is $npc:11000223$'s girlfriend $npc:11000224$ upset? Ride the cable car up to the restaurant in $map:02000135$ and ask her.

10001310-null-.name: 요정의 신발
10001310-null-.desc:
선량한 요정을 괴롭히는 나쁜 놈들…!
$map:02000041$의 몬스터들을 물리치고 $item:30000050$$pp:를,을$ 찾아주자.

10001310-null-NA.name: Twinkle Toes
10001310-null-NA.desc:
How dare they cause such trouble for the good fairies! It would be a shame to let such nice gifts go to waste.
Defeat the monsters in $map:02000041$ and find $item:30000050$.

10001320-null-.name: The Realest Estate
10001320-null-.desc:
$npc:11000185$ seems to always be busy since so many people are trying to buy and sell houses.
Let's go see $npc:11000246$ in $map:02000002$ and help her out.

10001321-null-.name: Now That's What I Call Labor
10001321-null-.desc:
It's not that difficult a task, and the pay seems to be pretty generous to boot.... Why don't I try packing and moving by going to $map:02000160$?
I can check the location of $map:02000160$ using the mini map of $map:02000002$.

10001322-null-.name: Prison Package
10001322-null-.desc:
$npc:11000401$ was so busy getting the comic books that he didn't notice that I was already inside packing the comic books that have already been piled up high.
Since I already agreed to help, I'll move the $item:30000124$ scattered around $npc:11000401$ to the yard.
10001322-null-.manual: Move the $item:30000124$ scattered around $npc:11000401$ to the yard

10001420-null-.name: Catch the Varaha
10001420-null-.desc:
Let's defeat $npc:22000002$, who appears sporadically in $map:02000087$, and claim the bounty.
He is just as ferocious as he is notorious, so it'd probably be a good idea team up with some other people to hunt it down.

10001430-null-.name: 칸토의 꿈
10001430-null-.desc:
$npc:22000002$에게 $item:30000065$$pp:를,을$ 빼앗긴 $npc:11000292$$pp:를,을$ 위해 $map:02000087$에서 $npc:22000002$$pp:가,이$ 나타날 때까지 기다렸다가 처치하자.
홀로 상대하기 어렵다면 함께 싸울 동료들을 모아보자.

10001430-null-NA.name: Kanto's Dream
10001430-null-NA.desc:
The $item:30000065$ is $npc:11000292$'s last shot at love, but it was stolen by $npc:22000002$. Wait for $npc:22000002$ to appear in $map:02000087$ and recover the potion for $npc:11000292$.

This will be a dangerous fight, so be sure to bring some friends!

10001450-null-NA.name: An Uncertain Fate
10001450-null-NA.desc: It might be fun to get your fortune read by $npc:11000283$ at $map:02000088$.

10001451-null-.name: 운명을 극복하는 자
10001451-null-.desc:
사실인지 아닌지 증명할 수는 없지만 어쩐지 운세를 듣고 보니 찜찜한 기분이다.
차라리 $item:30000068$$pp:를,을$ 구해서 찜찜한 기분은 시원하게 날려버리는 게 더 나을 것 같다.
$map:02000088$에서 $npc:23000020$$pp:를,을$ 만나면 뒷걸음질치지 말고 용감하게 달려들어서 처단하자.

10001451-null-NA.name: Overcoming Destiny
10001451-null-NA.desc:
No one can see the future. Not really. And yet, something about this fortune gnaws at the back of your mind...

Maybe you should get $item:30000068$, after all. Just in case.

10001460-null-.name: 아르웬과 유리구두
10001460-null-.desc:
$map:02000006$의 $npc:11000284$$pp:는,은$ 얼마 전 숲 속에서 몬스터의 습격을 받아 소중한 유리구두를 잃어버리고 말았다며 울고 있다. 
요정들은 반짝이는 아름다운 물건에 대한 집착이 대단하기 때문에 꼭 되찾고 싶어하는데… 
도와 주겠다고 나섰던 사람들이 모두 구두를 찾아주는 걸 포기할 정도로 찾기 어렵다는 $item:30000069$!
쉽게 포기하지 말고 $map:02000006$의 몬스터 중에서 $item:30000069$$pp:를,을$ 가지고 있는 녀석을 꼭 찾아내서 $npcName:11000284$$pp:가,이$ 환하게 웃을 수 있게 해 주자!

10001460-null-NA.name: Arwen's Glass Slippers
10001460-null-NA.desc:
You found $npc:11000284$ in $map:02000006$ bawling her little eyes out. Apparently her prized glass slippers were stolen by monsters. As everyone knows, fairies are extremely possessive of shiny baubles and things of beauty. Sadly, none of the people who offered to help her were able to follow through on their promise.

And so it falls to you to dry the tears in her eyes. Go forth and rough up the monsters of $map:02000006$ until one coughs up $npc:11000284$'s prized slippers!

10001470-null-.name: A Turtley Pure Love
10001470-null-.desc:
$npc:11000285$ planted the flowers in remembrance for his loved one, but is fed up with having monsters trample them to death. I was asked to help revive the flowers in $map:02000089$.
Let's help him with his request so that $npc:11000285$ can be at peace once more.

10001490-null-.name: 개구리 구출 대작전
10001490-null-.desc:
구리구리한 도마구리 녀석들이 $map:02000022$ 주변의 개구리들을 모두 잡아다가 싹쓸이를 하고 있다.
<font color="#ffd200">$npc:21090175$</font>, <font color="#ffd200">$npc:21090176$</font>, <font color="#ffd200">$npc:21090177$</font>$pp:를,을$ 처치하고 잡혀간 <font color="#ffd200">$item:30000071$</font>들을 찾아서 물가 연잎 위에 풀어주면 $npc:11000294$의 울음소리도 그칠 것 같다.
10001490-null-.manual: $map:02000022$의 도마구리들이 잡아간 $item:30000071$$pp:를,을$ 강가 연잎 위에 풀어주기

10001490-null-NA.name: Operation Frog Rescue
10001490-null-NA.desc: The 'gogs at the $map:02000022$ are on a campaign to wipe out the local frog population. Defeat $npcPlural:21090175$, $npcPlural:21090176$, and $npcPlural:21090177$, find the captured $itemPlural:30000071$, and return them to their lily pads.
10001490-null-NA.manual: Free $itemPlural:30000071$ from 'gogs at the $map:02000022$ and put them on lily pads

10001510-null-.name: 날아라, 나비야
10001510-null-.desc:
$npc:11000298$$pp:는,은$ $map:02000004$의 딱딱하게 굳어버린 장난감 나무 속에 나비들이 갇혀 있다며 발을 동동거린다.
날개가 있는 나비들이 훨훨 날 수 있도록 풀어주자.
10001510-null-.manual: 장난감 나무 속에 갇힌 나비 풀어주기

10001510-null-NA.name: Flight of the Butterflies
10001510-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000298$ says that there are butterflies trapped inside the petrified toy trees in $map:02000004$.

Release the butterflies so that they can fly free once more.
10001510-null-NA.manual: Free the butterflies trapped inside toy trees

10001520-null-.name: 농사꾼의 근심
10001520-null-.desc:
어느 날 $map:02000056$ 바닥에 의문의 균열이 생기면서부터  호수는 점점 루디브리엄 큐브로 변해가기 시작했다.
때문에 이곳에 사는 $npc:11000299$$pp:는,은$ 농작물에 물을 주지 못해 걱정이 이만저만이 아니다.
폭포 바닥에 조금씩 남아있는 물을 퍼서 양동이에 담아오자!
10001520-null-.manual: $map:02000056$의 폭포수 바닥에 남은 물을 양동이에 담기

10001520-null-NA.name: The Concerned Farmer
10001520-null-NA.desc:
The water of the basin in $map:02000056$'s ground has gradually begun to turn into ludibrium blocks, and $npc:11000299$ is worried about how he will water his crops.

Gather water from what remains of the basin below the waterfall.

10001521-null-.name: 당근당근, 행운당근
10001521-null-.desc:
여러 모로 $npc:11000299$의 걱정이 큰 것 같다.
그를 도와 $map:02000056$에 있는 당근 새싹에 물을 주자!

10001521-null-NA.name: A Load of Crop
10001521-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000299$ finally has some water for his crops, but too much ground to cover. Help him out by watering carrot sprouts in $map:02000056$!

10001522-null-.name: 당근을 지키는 기본적인 방법
10001522-null-.desc:
$npc:11000299$$pp:를,을$ 도와주긴 했지만 $map:02000056$의 몬스터들때문에 당근이 안전하게 잘 자라나지 못할 것 같다.
$map:02000056$의 몬스터들이 당근을 망치기 전에 먼저 녀석들을 처치하자!

10001522-null-NA.name: Champion of Carrots
10001522-null-NA.desc:
With a dash of water, $npc:11000299$'s crop will live another day—provided it's not eaten by monsters. 

Reduce the monster population in $map:02000056$ and protect the budding plants.

10001530-null-.name: All Sold Out
10001530-null-.desc: $npc:11000268$ is obsessed with money, wealth, and buying expensive things. She says that she needs $item:20000054$, but is unable to purchase it because it's constantly sold out in the shop. If I remember correctly, there are supposedly a lot of $npc:21000053$ in $map:02000173$ and $map:02000174$...
10001530-null-.manual: Gather $item:20000054$ around the Ant Tunnel area

10001531-null-.name: 소식 없는 보부상
10001531-null-.desc: $npc:11000268$에게 $item:20000075$$pp:를,을$ 구해오겠다고 호언장담하고 떠난 $npc:11000300$. 하지만 길을 떠난지 한참이 지났는데도 별다른 소식이 없다고 한다. $map:02000039$$pp2:로,으로$ 가서 $npc:11000300$$pp:를,을$ 찾아보자.

10001531-null-NA.name: The Missing Hawker
10001531-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000300$ went missing while collecting a $item:20000075$ for $npcName:11000268$. Go to $map:02000039$ and find him.

10001532-null-.name: 기운이 샘솟는 꼬리
10001532-null-.desc:
고소공포증 때문에 $map:02000039$에 있는 $npc:11000300$$pp:는,은$ 도저히 $map:02000052$$pp2:로,으로$ 뛰어내리지 못하겠다고 한다.
$map:02000039$에서 가장 높이 솟은 봉우리 꼭대기에서 끝이 보이지도 않는 $map:02000052$$pp2:로,으로$ 뛰어 내려야 하니, 고소공포증이 있는 사람들에게는 꽤 어려운 일로 여겨질 것 같다.
$npc:11000300$대신 $map:02000052$에서 $npc:22000005$$pp:를,을$ 처치하고 $item:20000075$$pp:를,을$ 구해오자!
홀로 상대하기 어렵다면 함께 싸울 동료들을 모아보자.

10001532-null-NA.name: The Tail Trade
10001532-null-NA.desc:
$npcName:11000300$ climbed the mountain peak at $map:02000039$, but he's too frightened to enter the $map:02000052$ due to his fear of heights. It's time for you to do $npcName:11000300$'s job and get the $item:20000075$ from $npcName:22000005$!

You might want to get some help for this one.

10001540-null-.name: 설계도면을 찾아라!
10001540-null-.desc:
$npc:11000134$의 부탁으로 $map:02000045$에 병참기지를 건설하고 있는 $npc:11000301$$pp:는,은$ 이곳 몬스터들에게 $item:30000077$$pp:를,을$ 도둑맞았다.
$map:02000045$의 몬스터들을 처치해서 $item:30000077$$pp:를,을$ 찾아오자.

10001540-null-NA.name: Misplaced Plans
10001540-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000301$ is building an outpost for $npc:11000134$ at $map:02000045$, but his $itemPlural:30000077$ were stolen from monsters. Round the monsters up and get the plans back.

10001541-null-.name: 일석이조 공사판
10001541-null-.desc:
$map:02000051$에 사는 $npc:11000271$$pp:는,은$ $item:30000015$$pp:를,을$ 찾고 있다고 한다.
흔하디 흔한 $item:30000015$$pp:를,을$ 모아서 어디에 쓰려고 하는 걸까?
일단, $map:02000045$ 곳곳 돌바위들을 파내고 그 아래에 있는 $item:30000015$$pp:를,을$ 모아서 $npc:11000271$에게 가져다 주자.

10001541-null-NA.name: Clumps for a Friend
10001541-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000271$ in $map:02000051$ is looking for $itemPlural:30000015$. Why could he possibly want such a thing? And how much will he pay for them? Find out by searching the rocks at the $map:02000045$ and going to him.

10001550-null-.name: Cursed Love
10001550-null-.desc:
Rumor has it that $npc:29000024$ will appear at the top of $map:02000046$ when all 4 of the altars are lighted.
Let's defeat $npc:29000024$ and take the $item:30000080$ that holds cursed power.

10001551-null-.name: Search and Seek
10001551-null-.desc: $npc:11000272$ of $map:02000051$ asked me to look for $npc:11000302$ in $map:02000046$.

10001560-null-.name: 메이플 연대기
10001560-null-.desc:
$npc:11000327$$pp:가,이$ $item:30000087$에서 확인하고 싶은 건 무엇이었을까?
$map:02000031$ 입구 쪽에 있는 책 수레에서 $item:30000087$$pp:를,을$ 찾아서 $map:02000001$에 있는 $npc:11000327$$pp:를,을$ 만나보자.

10001560-null-NA.name: Legends of Perion
10001560-null-NA.desc: On the way out of the library, you were tasked with delivering a copy of $item:30000087$ to $npcName:11000327$ in $map:02000001$. Hop to it!
10001560-null-NA.manual: Find $item:30000087$ in the book cart at the entrance of $map:02000031$

10001561-null-NA.name: More Than a Myth
10001561-null-NA.desc: It's time to unravel the mystery! Go to $map:02000076$ and meet with $npc:11000328$.

10001562-null-.name: 소몰이 기행
10001562-null-.desc:
$npc:11000328$$pp:는,은$ 지난날 $npc:11000039$에게 들었었던 $npc:21000425$에 관한 전설을 들려주었다.
$npc:21000225$$pp:를,을$ 잡다보면 아주 가끔 얻을 수 있다는 $item:30000088$부터 구해서 전설이 사실인지 확인해봐야겠다.
$map:02000056$$pp2:로,으로$ 가서 이 근방에 자주 출몰하는 $npc:21000225$$pp:를,을$ 찾아보자.

10001562-null-NA.name: Unmasking the Past
10001562-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000328$ told you the legend of $npc:21000425$ as he heard it from $npc:11000039$. To find out whether it's true, you'll need to get your hands on a $item:30000088$ recently liberated from a tourist shop by the $npcPlural:21000225$ of $map:02000056$.

10001563-null-.name: 전설은 살아있다
10001563-null-.desc:
$map:02000060$ 서쪽 바위 언덕 어디쯤엔가 그 입구가 있다는 $map:02000047$!!
$item:30000088$$pp:를,을$ 가지고 $map:02000047$$pp2:로,으로$ 가서 제단을 찾아 그 뒤쪽 벽에 $item:30000088$$pp:를,을$ 걸어보자. 고대 사원이니만큼 어떤 위험이 도사리고 있을지 모르니 주변을 잘 둘러보면서 이동하는 것이 좋겠다.

10001563-null-NA.name: The Legend Lives
10001563-null-NA.desc:
$map:02000047$'s entrance is somewhere near the rocky hills in the western side of $map:02000060$! If you go there and hang the $item:30000088$ on the altar, you should be able to once and all put this myth to rest.

Where you're going is a dangerous place. Tread carefully!

10001570-null-.name: 최첨단 로봇 메이드
10001570-null-.desc:
$map:02000163$에서 만난 $npc:11001031$$pp:는,은$ 연구소 로봇들이 갑자기 이상 작동을 하며 연구원들을 공격하기 시작했다고 말하며, 로봇들에게 붙잡혀 있는 $npc:11000335$$pp:를,을$ 구해주면 $item:30000084$$pp:를,을$ 꺼낼 수 있는 $item:30000083$$pp:를,을$ 얻을 수 있을 것이라고 했다.
$map:02000163$에서 $npc:11000335$$pp:를,을$ 구해주고, $item:30000083$$pp:를,을$ 얻어 $npc:11000244$$pp:가,이$ 주문한 $item:30000084$$pp:를,을$ 찾아가자.

10001570-null-NA.name: Robots Running Amuck
10001570-null-NA.desc: $npc:11001031$ from the $map:02000163$ says that the robots in the lab are malfunctioning. To get the $item:30000084$, you'll first need to free $npc:11000335$ and obtain his $item:30000083$. Then you can retrieve the $item:30000084$ and for $npc:11000244$.
10001570-null-NA.manual: Free $npc:11000335$ at the $map:02000163$ to get the master key card|Retrieve the $item:30000084$ from the $map:02000163$

10001571-null-.name: 특별한 하녀
10001571-null-.desc:
$npc:11000335$에게 무슨 일이 생긴 것은 아닐까?
$map:02000163$$pp2:로,으로$ 가서 상황을 알아보자.

10001571-null-NA.name: A Match Maid in Heaven
10001571-null-NA.desc: What's holding up $npc:11000335$? Head to $map:02000163$ and see what you can find out.

10001590-null-.name: 내겐 너무 높은 길
10001590-null-.desc:
$npc:11000338$$pp:는,은$ 바퀴가 빠져 뒤집어져버린 수레에 담긴 빵 상자를 절벽 위 호텔 앞으로 옮겨 달라고 부탁해왔다.
얼핏 보기에도 $npc:11000338$의 몸으로는 빵 상자를 들고 가파르고 좁은 계단을 올라가기는 힘들 것 같다. 운동하는 셈 치고 그의 부탁을 들어주자.
$map:02000178$$pp:는,은$ $npc:11000338$ 앞에 있는 가파른 계단을 따라 올라가면 그 꼭대기에 위치하고 있다.

10001590-null-NA.name: Up and Down, Up and Down
10001590-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000338$'s bread cart flipped over, and he needs you to carry his delicious bread to $map:02000178$ at the top of a steep set of stairs.

10001591-null-.name: 달콤한 유혹
10001591-null-.desc:
$npc:11000339$$pp:가,이$ 피하려는 것을 보니 $npc:11000340$$pp:는,은$ 과하게 깐깐한 인물인 듯 하다.
$map:02000178$ 구경도 할 겸 $npcName:11000339$$pp:가,이$ 건네 준 머핀을 들고 $npc:11000340$$pp:를,을$ 만나볼까?

10001591-null-NA.name: The Heavenly Scent of Bread
10001591-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000339$ is trying to avoid $npc:11000340$'s wrath, so he sends you to deliver a Bread Sample in his stead.

10001610-null-.name: A Tragic Decision
10001610-null-.desc:
When $npc:11000027$ tried to help a young child that was having his soul being slowly eaten away by an evil spirit, his friends also became corrupted by the dark aura.
$npcName:11000027$ blames himself for exposing his friends to the darkness, and pleads that you free their souls.
Let's go to $map:02000053$, where the $npc:21000109$ corrupted by dark aura are located, and release the souls of $npcName:11000027$'s friends.
10001610-null-.manual: Defeat $npc:21000109$ in $map:02000053$ to liberate the unicorns' souls

10001620-null-.name: 납골당의 비밀
10001620-null-.desc:
$map:02000059$에 있는 $map:02000082$에서 $npc:22000011$$pp:가,이$ 나타났다는 신고를 받고 $npc:11000015$$pp:는,은$ 정예 정찰대를 꾸려 $npc:22000011$$pp:를,을$ 찾아 나섰지만 수차례 실패했다며 고심하고 있다.
오랫동안 사람의 발길이 끊겼던 $map:02000082$, 그 깊은 곳에서 나타난 $npc:22000011$$pp:는,은$ 그 모습을 감췄다가 나타나길 반복하고 있는 듯한데… 
$npcName:11000015$의 말대로 주민들의 안전과 메이플 월드를 위해서라도 $map:02000082$에서 $npc:22000011$$pp:를,을$ 만나면, 그 즉시 처치하고 위험한 도끼를 빼앗는 것이 좋겠다.

10001620-null-NA.name: A Rotten Malcontent
10001620-null-NA.desc:
After reports of a $npc:22000011$ menacing the people of $map:02000059$, $npc:11000015$ has tasked you with tracking down the undead assailant.

$npc:22000011$ was last seen near the $map:02000082$. Defeat him and recover his axe, for the safety of the people!

10001630-null-.name: Let Me Axe You a Question

10001631-null-.name: Discovering the Truth
10001631-null-.desc: $npc:11000203$ wanted to know the reason why $npc:21000041$ stole the tree cutters' axes, and impaled it in their own bodies to become $npc:21000045$. I was asked to go to $npc:11000328$ in $map:02000076$ and discover the truth behind this strange phenomenon.

10001632-null-.name: Axe-amine the Stumps
10001632-null-.desc:
Who is the little girl that persuaded $npc:11000134$ with tears in her eyes to save $npc:21000041$?
I'll go to $map:02000076$ and ask $npc:11000001$ for more answers.

10001633-null-.name: QUESTDESCRIPTION_10001633_NAME
10001633-null-.desc:
Wait, it's $npc:11000188$... Isn't she the older sister of $npc:11000186$ who unfroze and saved?!
If what $npc:11000001$ says is true...could $npc:21000041$ have waited with an axe stuck on its head this whole time, waiting for $npc:11000188$, who couldn't go because she was frozen?
I'll try to think this through while I meet with $npc:11000188$ in $map:02000085$.

10001634-null-.name: QUESTDESCRIPTION_10001634_NAME
10001634-null-.desc:
After hearing $npc:21000045$'s story, $npc:11000188$ was obviously extremely sad and heartbroken.
Let's go to $map:02000059$ and relay $npc:11000188$'s message to $npc:11000203$ in her stead, as she has not yet fully recovered.

10001650-null-.name: Risky Business
10001650-null-.desc:
$npc:11000307$, who runs an interior shop in $map:02000119$, asks that I collect the Ludibrium meteoric fragments that fell on the back hill, claiming that the fragments can be used as a new materials when they are refined.
Let's go to $map:02000014$ and collect those fragments.

10001670-null-.name: 푸딩은 사랑을 싣고
10001670-null-.desc:
친절한 $npc:11000002$ 아줌마는 $map:02000017$에서 집을 짓고 있다는 $npc:11000350$에게 갓 만든 푸딩을 전해 달라고 부탁했다. $map:02000001$에서 멀지 않은 곳이라고 했으니까 금방 찾아갈 수 있겠지?
$map:02000017$$pp2:로,으로$ 가서 $npc:11000350$$pp:를,을$ 찾아보자.

10001670-null-NA.name: For the Love of Pudding
10001670-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000002$ heard her friend $npcName:11000350$ was building a home in $map:02000017$ and asked you to deliver some pudding as a housewarming gift.

She said $map:02000001$ is close by, so it should be a quick trip. Find $npc:11000350$ at $map:02000017$.

10001680-null-.name: 숲을 살려라!
10001680-null-.desc:
$map:02000017$$pp:를,을$ 지키는 $npc:11000368$$pp:는,은$ 인간들이 드나들면서 숲의 모습을 잃어버린 $map:02000041$$pp:가,이$ 예전으로 돌아가길 바라고 있다. 
그래서 꼬깔나무 묘목들을 심었지만, 돌바위 아래 숨어 사는 꿈틀꿈틀 나무벌레 $npc:29000022$들이 나무뿌리를 갉아먹는 바람에 나무들이 모두 죽을 위기에 처했다며 $npc:29000022$들을 처치해달라고 부탁했다.
$map:02000041$$pp2:로,으로$ 가서 꼬깔나무 주변의 돌바위를 걷어내고 나무벌레 $npc:29000022$$pp:를,을$ 찾아서 처치하자.

10001680-null-NA.name: Only You Can Preserve the Forest
10001680-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000368$, the guardian of $map:02000017$, wishes for $map:02000041$ to return to its past glory... the way it was before the humans came. He planted lots of trees, but the pesky tree bugs known as $npcPlural:29000022$ keep eating them.

Help $npc:11000368$'s by searching under wrocks in $map:02000041$ and taking care of any $npcPlural:29000022$ you find.
10001680-null-NA.manual: Eliminate the $npcPlural:29000022$ hiding underneath the rocks in $map:02000041$

10001730-null-.name: 차우에게 맞서는 자
10001730-null-.desc:
한번 걸리면 뼈와 살이 분리될 정도의 아픔을 겪을 수 있다는 $npc:22300105$!
$npc:11000150$$pp:는,은$ $npc:22300105$$pp:가,이$ 얼마나 강한지 알고 싶으면 직접 부딪혀보라고 말했다.
$map:02000083$에서 $npc:22300105$$pp:가,이$ 나타나길 기다렸다가 그와 맞서 싸워보자.
홀로 상대하기 어려울 수 있으니 마음이 맞는 동료들과 함께 힘을 합하는 것이 좋을 것 같다.

10001730-null-NA.name: Rise Against
10001730-null-NA.desc:
They say $npc:22300105$ redefines the meaning of pain to everyone who has the misfortune to meet him.
$npc:11000150$ has challenged you to face $npc:22300105$ one-on-one to see how strong he really is. It sounds like he hangs around $map:02000083$.
He's definitely a challenge to face alone, so you should probably bring some allies with you.

10001760-null-.name: 반격의 힘
10001760-null-.desc:
$map:02000181$의 $npc:11000404$$pp:는,은$ 블루 라펜타가 깨진 후 $map:02000181$에서 깨어난 $npc:23000024$$pp:가,이$ 자신의 아버지와 친구들을 모두 해쳤다며 복수를 해달라고 부탁했다.
블루 라펜타가 깨짐과 동시에 깨어나 온갖 횡포를 부리고 있는 $npc:23000024$!!
$npc:11000404$의 개인적인 원한이 아니더라도 메이플 월드를 위협하는 위험한 존재이므로 처치하는 것이 좋겠다.
$npc:11000404$의 충고대로 뜻을 같이하는 동료들을 모아 힘을 합해 함께 싸우도록 하자.

10001760-null-NA.name: Free Gift with Vengeance
10001760-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000404$ at $map:02000181$ says that $npc:23000024$, who awoke after the Blue Lapenta shattered, slew his papa. He wants vengeance! Defeat $npc:23000024$ for justice! And also for the free gift...

10001790-null-.name: 해변에 사는 내 친구
10001790-null-.desc:
$map:02000086$에서 일하고 있는 $npc:11000360$$pp:는,은$ 친구 $npc:11000420$$pp:가,이$ $map:02000111$$pp:는,은$ 편안하고 안전해서 엄마와 함께 살기 참 좋은 곳이라며 이사를 권유했지만, 밀린 일거리가 많아서 쉽사리 자리를 비울 수가 없다고 한다.
$npc:11000360$$pp:를,을$ 대신해 $map:02000111$$pp2:로,으로$ 가서, 그 곳이 정말 $npc:11000360$$pp:가,이$ 엄마와 함께 살기에 적합한 곳인지 살펴보자.

10001790-null-NA.name: By the Seaside
10001790-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000360$'s friend, $npc:11000420$, recommended that $npc:11000360$ and his mother move to $map:02000111$, since it's a beautiful, safe, and comfortable place to have a home. But $npc:11000360$ says that he's swamped with work and doesn't have time to check the place out right now.
Go to $map:02000111$ and scope the place out.

10001791-null-.name: 생존경쟁
10001791-null-.desc:
언젠가부터 $map:02000111$에 나타나 사람들을 괴롭히고 있다는 $npc:23000018$!
$map:02000111$에서 한 번씩 출몰한다는 이 녀석 때문에 $npc:11000421$$pp:는,은$ 생계가 곤란할 정도로 장사에 어려움을 겪고 있다.
전략을 잘 세워서 $map:02000111$에 나타난 $npc:23000018$$pp:를,을$ 처치해 보자!
혼자서 녀석을 상대하기 힘들다면 주변의 동료들과 함께 힘을 합쳐서 싸우도록 하자.

10001791-null-NA.name: Struggling to Survive
10001791-null-NA.desc:
A $npc:23000018$ is wreaking havoc on the beaches of $map:02000111$, and $npc:11000421$'s business is struggling to stay afloat.

Dispatch the $npc:23000018$ at $map:02000111$! Be warned, it's best to bring friends when facing a foe this fierce!

10001800-null-.name: 불량 대출자
10001800-null-.desc:
$npc:11000002$의 귀여운 아들 $npc:11000055$$pp:는,은$ $map:02000001$에서 $map:02000031$에 가장 많이 드나드는 꼬마다. 하지만 늘 대출기한을 어겨 $npc:11000005$의 머리를 아프게 하는 녀석이기도 하다.
$map:02000001$에서 $npc:11000055$$pp:를,을$ 찾아서 빌려간 책의 대출기한이 지났다는 사실을 알려주자.

10001800-null-NA.name: Borrower's Remorse
10001800-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000055$, $npc:11000002$'s lovely son, is a frequent visitor to $map:02000031$. However, he's a bit of a headache for $npc:11000005$, as he rarely returns his books.

Find $npc:11000055$ in $map:02000001$ and inform him that he should check out a book on manners once he returns the last book he borrowed.

10001801-null-.name: 숲의 전설
10001801-null-.desc:
그저 옛날 이야기책 속에서 전해오는 전설인 줄만 알았던 $npc:22000003$$pp:와,과$ $npc:22000004$… 
그녀들이 이 세계 어딘가에 실제로 존재한다면 그 전설 같은 이야기도 사실인 것이 되는데… 
$map:02000001$의 $npc:11000327$$pp:를,을$ 찾아가서 정말 그녀들이 나타난 것인지, 어디에 나타난 것인지 물어보자.

10001801-null-NA.name: Forest Legends and Folktales
10001801-null-NA.desc:
$npc:22000003$ and $npc:22000004$ were supposed to be just a creepy campfire story... But if they're real, how many other legends could be true?
You should find $npc:11000327$ in $map:02000001$ to ask if they really did reappear. And if so, where?

10001802-null-.name: 비극을 부른 사랑
10001802-null-.desc:
$npc:11000327$$pp:는,은$ $map:02000041$에서 목격된 $npc:22000003$$pp:와,과$ $npc:22000004$$pp:가,이$ 진짜일 가능성을 염두에 두고, 그녀들이 정말 알베르토가 로안나에게 사랑의 증표로 선물한  루비 목걸이와 보석함을 가지고 있는지 확인해보고 싶다며 도움을 요청했다.
$map:02000041$$pp2:로,으로$ 가서 $npc:22000003$$pp:와,과$ $npc:22000004$$pp:가,이$ 정말 나타나는지, 그녀들이 루비 목걸이와 보석함을 가지고 있는지 확인해보자.
그녀들의 악명은 근거없는 소문은 아닐테니 서로 힘을 합할 수 있는 동료들을 구해서 함께 싸우는 것이 좋겠다.

10001802-null-NA.name: A Tragic Love
10001802-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000327$ has asked you to investigate whether $npc:22000003$ and $npc:22000004$, elves mentioned in an old folktale, have actually returned to $map:02000041$, and whether they possess the trinkets Alberto gave to Roanna to confess his love.

Travel to $map:02000041$ and find out! If the tales are true, you'll want to bring allies to aid you in battle.
10001802-null-NA.manual: (Elite) Defeat $npc:22000003$ and obtain $item:30000131$|(Elite) Defeat $npc:22000004$ and obtain $item:30000132$

10001803-null-.name: 슬픈 연인의 무덤
10001803-null-.desc:
$map:02000001$의 $npc:11000327$$pp:는,은$ $map:02000017$ 북서쪽 큰 나무줄기 위 어딘가에 로안나의 무덤이 있다며, 그 앞에  $item:30000133$$pp:를,을$ 놓아 달라고 부탁했다.
$map:02000017$에서 로안나의 무덤을 찾아보자.

10001803-null-NA.name: Bury Your Love
10001803-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000327$ of $map:02000001$ has asked that you leave $item:30000133$ at her grave, which is located somewhere in the treetops in the northwest of $map:02000017$.

10001804-null-.name: 하늘에서라도, 부디…
10001804-null-.desc:
$map:02000017$ 깊은 곳에 자리잡고 있는 $npc:11000422$!
그 곁에는 알베르토의 것으로 추정되는 백골이 지키고 있었다. 로안나와 알베르토의 사랑이 하늘에서라도 행복하게 맺어질 수 있도록 기도하며, $npc:11000327$에게 받아 온 $item:30000133$$pp:를,을$ $npc:11000422$ 앞에 놓아두자.

10001804-null-NA.name: Those We Leave Behind
10001804-null-NA.desc:
You found $npc:11000422$ located deep in the $map:02000017$. Alongside it was a nameless marker for a grave that could only belong to Alberto.

You should leave $item:30000133$ in front of her grave, in hopes that it brings her some peace in the afterlife.
10001804-null-NA.manual: Place the jewel box in front of $npc:11000422$ in $map:02000017$

10001820-null-.name: 독수리를 붙잡고
10001820-null-.desc:
$map:02000085$의 $npc:11000425$$pp:는,은$ 날아다니는 야생 독수리를 붙잡고 건너편에 있는 $npc:11000427$에게 $item:30000141$$pp:를,을$ 전해달라고 부탁했다.
야생 독수리 붙잡기라… 꽤 재미있을 것 같다.
$npc:11000425$ 옆에서 야생 독수리가 올 때까지 기다렸다가 붙잡고 날아보자.

10001820-null-NA.name: Fly Like a Vulture
10001820-null-NA.desc:
Afraid of plummeting to his death, $npc:11000425$ asked you to deliver the $item:30000141$ to $npc:11000427$ in $map:02000085$. All you have to do is grab onto a vulture and let it fly you to your destination.

You should wait near $npc:11000425$ for a vulture to arrive, and grab on tight.
10001820-null-NA.complete: Grab hold of a vulture in $map:02000085$ and fly to $npc:11000427$

10001821-null-.name: 분노의 날갯짓
10001821-null-.desc:
$npc:11000427$$pp:는,은$ $map:02000085$ 고지대 평원에 있는 독수리 알들이 무사히 부화할 수 있도록 $npc:23000019$$pp:가,이$ 나타나면 사람들과 함께 힘을 합해서 처치하는 데 힘을 보태달라고 부탁해왔다.
$npc:23000019$의 거대한 날개도 붙잡고 날 수 있을까?
$map:02000085$에 $npc:23000019$$pp:가,이$ 나타나면 주변 사람들과 힘을 합해 함께 처치해보자.

10001821-null-NA.name: Wings of Rage
10001821-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000427$ wants to train the vulture hatchlings on the highland plains of $map:02000085$ as transportation for the local populace, but $npc:23000019$ keeps destroying all the eggs.

Work alongside other adventurers to defeat $npc:23000019$ in $map:02000085$ when it finally appears.

10001840-null-.name: 난파선의 흔적
10001840-null-.desc:
$map:02000062$의 $npc:11000025$$pp:는,은$ 그녀의 오빠 $npc:11000021$$pp:가,이$ $map:63000001$$pp:를,을$ 떠나 $map:02000062$$pp2:로,으로$ 오는 길에 폭풍우에 휩쓸려 배가 난파된 후로 실종되어 소식이 없다며 발을 동동 굴렀다.
$map:02000183$$pp2:로,으로$ 가서 $npc:11000021$의 생사라도 알아봐 달라는 그녀의 간절한 부탁을 매몰차게 거절할 수는 없을 것 같다.
$map:02000062$ 부둣가에서 잡다한 일을 도맡아 하는 $npc:11000994$에게 부탁하면 다소 위험하지만 $map:02000183$$pp2:로,으로$ 빠른 시간 안에 도착할 수 있는 배를 태워줄 수 있다고 하니 그를 찾아가 보는 것도 좋겠다.

10001840-null-NA.name: Searching the Wreckage
10001840-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000025$ in $map:02000062$ is worried about her older brother, $npcName:11000021$, who disappeared during a typhoon on his way to visit her from $map:63000001$. She wants you to head to $map:02000183$, where the wreckage of his boat was found, to investigate. She says $npcName:11000994$ down by the docks might be able to get you to the island quickly.

10001841-null-.name: 바다의 유령선
10001841-null-.desc:
$map:02000183$에서 우연히 만난 $npc:11000782$!
유령 해적단에게 붙잡혀 죽을 고비를 넘긴 모험담을 듣는 도중 $npc:11000021$의 소식을 알게 되었다.
다행히 살아있다는 $npc:11000021$! $npc:11000025$에게 기쁜 소식을 전해줄 수 있을 것 같다.
$map:02000067$$pp2:로,으로$ 가서 $npc:11000021$$pp:를,을$ 만나보자.

10001841-null-NA.name: Undead Pirates
10001841-null-NA.desc: You found $npcName:11000782$ at $map:02000183$, who told you about a frightening experience with undead pirates, during which you found out that $npcName:11000021$ is alive! $npc:11000025$ will be so happy! Time to go find $npcName:11000021$ at $map:02000067$.

10001842-null-.name: 산티아고가 겪은 일
10001842-null-.desc: $npc:11000021$$pp:는,은$ $map:63000001$$pp:를,을$ 떠나 유령 해적선에서 탈출해 나오기까지의 기적같은 일화를 들려주었다. 겨우 꼬리가 잡힌 유령 해적선! 과연 실종된 빅토리아호의 진실을 밝히는 불씨가 될 수 있을까?

10001842-null-NA.name: Santiago's Story
10001842-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000021$ shares a terrifying tale of undead pirates and a grand escape from a phantom pirate ship. Could this be the first major clue to finding the truth behind what happened to the Victoria?

10001850-null-.name: 합격 소식
10001850-null-.desc:
$npc:11000476$$pp:는,은$ 골두스 택배 기사들의 파업으로 인턴 사원 서류 합격자들에게 직접 돌아다니면서 합격 소식을 전하다가 발을 다쳐서 걸을 수가 없는 상태라고 한다.
면접 일정이 시작되기 전에 마지막 합격자인 $map:02000166$의 $npc:11001054$에게 합격 소식과 면접 안내를 해야 하는데… $npc:11000476$$pp:를,을$ 대신해서 $map:02000166$의 $npc:11001054$에게 합격 소식을 전해주자.

10001850-null-NA.name: A Timely Interview
10001850-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000476$ hurt her feet delivering interview requests to prospective interns, but she still has one left to deliver to $npc:11001054$ in $map:02000166$...

Lucky for her, you've agreed to go in her place.

10001851-null-.name: 합격 기원
10001851-null-.desc: 합격 소식을 들은 $npc:11001054$$pp:는,은$ 기쁨을 감추지 못했다. 하지만 그것도 잠시… 피자 배달 아르바이트 때문에 $npc:11001054$$pp:는,은$ 면접을 보지 못할 수도 있다고 한다. $npc:11001054$$pp:가,이$ 무사히 면접을 볼 수 있도록 그를 대신해서 $map:52000004$ 1층에 있는 피자를 꼭대기 층까지 배달하도록 하자.

10001851-null-NA.name: A Difficult Delivery
10001851-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11001054$ is ecstatic to be considered for the Goldus intrernship. But with his part-time pizza delivery job, there's no way he can make it to the interview... 

Thankfully for him, that's where you come in! Deliver the pizzas sitting at the first floor of $map:52000004$ to the top floor in $npc:11001054$'s place.
10001851-null-NA.manual: Take the pizza from $map:52000004$ 1F and deliver it to the top floor
10001851-null-NA.complete: Find $npc:11001055$ at the top floor of $map:52000004$

10001852-null-.name: 꿈을 향해서
10001852-null-.desc:
다행히 $npc:11001054$$pp:는,은$ 1차 면접까지 무난하게 통과한 모양이다. 하지만 최종 관문인 "$npc:11000252$ 앞에서 골두스 찬양가 부르기"가 남아있는데, 노래 가사를 도통 외울 수가 없다며 울상이다.
$npc:11001054$$pp:가,이$ 골두스 찬양가를 편한 마음으로 잘 외울 수 있도록 그를 대신해서 $map:52000004$ 1층에 있는 피자를 꼭대기 층까지 배달하도록 하자.

10001852-null-NA.name: 30 Minutes or Less
10001852-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11001054$ seems to have made it through the first round of interviews, but there's no time to prepare for the second one while fulfilling his delivery obligations. 

Lucky for him, you've agreed to take the pizzas from the first floor of $map:52000004$ and deliver them to the roof so that $npc:11001054$ can prepare with peace of mind.
10001852-null-NA.manual: Take the pizza from $map:52000004$ 1F and deliver it to the top floor
10001852-null-NA.complete: Find $npc:11001055$ at the top floor of $map:52000004$

10001853-null-.name: Unidentified Thieving Assailant
10001853-null-.desc:
$npc:11001028$ of $map:02000309$ said that the results from the study regarding the principles of time, $item:30000320$, $item:30000321$, and $item:30000322$ all disappeared after an invasion by an unknown assailant.
$map:02000298$ in $map:02000259$ is the place where the Chaos Time Key is the most useful!
By using the $npc:11001056$ located behind $npc:11001028$, teleport to $map:02000259$ and assess the situation at $map:02000298$!

10001854-null-.name: Dungeon: Hacker’s Ambush
10001854-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:21008001$ 
(Entrance: $map:2000259$)
Party Size (4 players)

$npc:11001057$ of $map:02000259$ said that this hacker group appeared out of nowhere and overtook $map:02000298$. Stop this army of hackers and investigate the perilous situation at $map:02000299$.
10001854-null-.manual: Stop the hacker group Funny Fingers in $map:02000298$ | Investigate $map:02000299$

10001855-null-.name: Dungeon: Protect the Time Hole!
10001855-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:2000298$ 
(Entrance: $map:2000259$)
Party Size (4 players)

$npc:11001057$ in $map:02000259$ said that the unidentified assailant who took the Chaos Time Key must be stopped from seizing the universe's center of time. $npc:11001057$ said that this unknown attacker will be found at $map:02000298$ as a result of the unstable time traveling process, and must be stopped in order to protect $map:02000304$'s safety.
10001855-null-.manual: Find $map:02000304$ in $map:02000298$ | (Elite) Find and stop the unidentified assailant with the Chaos Time Key

10001860-null-.name: 설렘만 남기고…
10001860-null-.desc:
$map:02000001$의 잡화상인 $npc:11000010$$pp:는,은$ 그녀의 마음 속에 설렘만 남겨두고 사라져버린 갈색 삿갓을 쓴 남자를 찾고 있다.
떠돌이 보부상으로부터 개미굴 쪽에서 그와 비슷한 모습의 사람을 보았다는 이야기를 듣고 $npc:11000010$$pp:는,은$ 개미굴에서 그를 찾아봐 달라는 부탁을 했다.
항상 도도하고 시크한 $npc:11000010$$pp:를,을$ 이렇게 풋풋하고 여린 여자로 바꿔버린 갈색 삿갓을 쓴 사나이의 정체가 뭘까?
$map:02000173$에서부터 그의 행적을 찾아보자.
10001860-null-.complete: $map:02000173$에서 갈색 삿갓을 쓴 남자 행적 추적하기

10001860-null-NA.name: Utterly Charmed
10001860-null-NA.desc:
$npcName:11000010$ of $map:02000001$ has fallen head-over-heels for a man with a bamboo hat. Unfortunately, he vanished without warning. She's heard rumors that a man matching his description was spotted near the Ant Tunnel.

Head to the $map:02000173$ and get some answers.
10001860-null-NA.complete: Search for the man in the bamboo hat at the $map:02000173$

10001861-null-.name: 추억으로 살다
10001861-null-.desc:
$map:02000173$에서 갈색 삿갓을 쓴 남자 대신 요상한 플라스틱을 눈에 달고 있는 $npc:11000145$라는 자를 만났다.
그의 말에 따르면 $npc:22000322$에게 죽을 뻔한 자기를 밀쳐내고 싸운 사람이 $item:11300119$$pp:를,을$ 쓰고 있었다는데… 
$npc:11000010$에게 종이꽃만을 남긴 채 떠난 그 남자는 어떻게 된 것일까…?
$map:02000173$에서 $npc:22000322$$pp:를,을$ 찾아다니다 보면 그의 행적을 알 수 있지 않을까?

10001861-null-NA.name: Memory of the Man
10001861-null-NA.desc:
Instead of finding the man in the bamboo hat, you found a strange fellow wearing a high-tech monocle: $npc:11000145$. He claims that the man who saved his life from a $npcName:22000322$ was wearing a $item:11300119$ and left an origami flower behind. It must be the same man that $npcName:11000010$ told you about!

Maybe you'll find another clue if you find the $npcName:22000322$ in the $map:02000173$.

10002151-null-.name: The Power of the Wind
10002151-null-.desc:
$npc:11000304$ wants the power to control the wind!
She needs $npc:22000007$'s $item:30000186$.
Let's take $item:30000186$ when $map:02000180$'s $npc:22000007$ appears.

10002230-null-.name: The Hunt for Comrades
10002230-null-.desc: $npc:11000842$ asked me to go to $map:03000143$ and deliver a message to a companion.

10002231-null-.name: Preparation Before Perspiration
10002231-null-.desc:
$npc:11000841$ was injured and was treated by a doctor at an emergency shelter. However, the wounds unfortunately became worse, and as a result, $npc:11000841$ is now immobile. The Lumina Liberation Army's Katramus operation to rescue citizens must be executed without any issues...
I'll go to $map:03000057$ in $npc:11000841$'s place to remove the poisoned traps near Katramus and defeat $npc:29000049$!
10002231-null-.manual: Remove the poisoned traps near $map:03000057$ Katramus | Defeat $map:03000057$'s $npc:29000049$

10002232-null-.name: Dungeon: The Mining Captives
10002232-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:21009001$ 
(Entrance: $map:3000057$)
Party Size (4 players)

After sharing an entrance to infiltrate $map:02000292$, $npc:11000839$ said that it would be best to rescue the citizens trapped in $map:02000292$ before the Lumina Liberation Army's plan rolls into action.
It would be a big help if I could free at least a few more people from the suffering as soon as possible.
Time to gather companions to help free the captured citizens in $map:02000292$!

10002233-null-.name: Dungeon: The Taskmaster
10002233-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:21009001$ 
(Entrance: $map:3000057$)
Party Size (4 players)

$npc:11000839$ shared the stories of the rescued people of $map:02000292$ and said that the plans of the Lumina Liberation Army will be expedited.
It's time to assist the Lumina Liberation Army in conquering Katramus, rescuing all the citizens, then finally defeating the evil taskmaster $npc:24000516$!

10002234-null-.name: Dungeon: A Mother's Trace
10002234-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:21009001$ 
(Entrance: $map:3000057$)
Party Size (4 players)

$npc:11000186$, whom I previously met at $map:02000085$, told me with tears in his eyes that his older sister has been suffering with nightmares ever since they heard about Katramus from the Land of Darkness.
Are the rumors about $npc:11000186$'s parents being held as slaves at Katramus really true? Keeping in mind that $npc:11000186$ and $npc:11000188$'s mother is wearing a silver bracelet with her initials on it, I can attempt to pinpoint her location at Katramus!
10002234-null-.manual: (Elite) Find the silver bracelet of $npc:11000188$'s mother at Katramus

10002240-null-.name: Dungeon: More Than a Feeling
10002240-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:21002001$ 
(Entrance: $map:2000172$)
Party Size (4 players)

While observing the forest with a telescope, $map:02000172$'s $npc:11000873$ spotted a green tornado beyond a rather peculiar door, and asked me to find out what exactly is happening beyond said door.

10002260-null-.name: Eagle Eye News
10002260-null-.desc: $map:02000146$'s $npc:11000009$ said that Murpagoth's eagle from $map:02000051$ flew over to deliver $npc:11000064$'s news.

10002261-null-.name: Onward to Perion
10002261-null-.desc: $map:02000153$'s $npc:11000215$ told me to go to $map:02000051$ first and find out what happened.
10002261-null-.complete: Go to $map:02000051$ and discover what happened

10002262-null-.name: Trivial Treasure
10002262-null-.desc: $map:02000051$'s $npc:11000136$ told me that more detailed information could be learned from $npc:11000078$ at $map:02000170$.

10002264-null-.name: Eye of Fire
10002264-null-.desc: $map:02000049$'s $npc:11000039$ told me to place 50 $item:30000001$ into the jar on the altar behind him and chant the incantation "Yaramachata charamayata."
10002264-null-.manual: Make $item:30000201$ by chanting the incantation to the jar on the altar

10002280-null-.name: 예전의 내가 아니야!
10002280-null-.desc: 건달 세계에서 발을 빼겠다며 남은 인생에서 절대 주먹을 휘두르지 않겠다고 다짐한 $map:02000110$의 $npc:11000358$$pp:는,은$ 자신을 대신해서 위험한 폭탄을 닥치는대로 던지고 다니는 $npc:21000281$들을 혼내 달라는 부탁을 했다.

10002280-null-NA.name: Reinvented
10002280-null-NA.desc: Having sworn to leave the thug life behind and never use his fists again, $npc:11000358$'s upset that he can't do anything about the $npcPlural:21000281$. They're throwing dangerous bombs everywhere, and he's asked you to put a stop to it.

10002360-null-.name: 시계탑 속으로
10002360-null-.desc: $npc:11000870$$pp:는,은$ 시계탑의 시계가 멈춘 원인을 파악하기 위해 $map:02000161$$pp:로,으로$ 들어간 $npc:11000871$$pp:가,이$ 감감 무소식이라며 상황을 파악해 달라고 부탁한다.

10002360-null-NA.name: Tick Tock Clock Tower
10002360-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000870$ has asked you to help solve the mystery of the stopped Clock Tower. Head into the $map:02000161$ to find $npc:11000871$.

10002361-null-.name: 아수라장 놀이터
10002361-null-.desc:
$npc:11000871$$pp:는,은$ 시계를 굴리는 거대한 토끼가 낚아채 간 $item:39000026$$pp:를,을$ 찾아 달라고 한다.
$map:02000161$를 가득 채운 몬스터들을 처치하며 거대한 토끼를 찾아서 $item:39000026$$pp:를,을$ 되찾자!
10002361-null-.manual: $map:02000161$의 몬스터 처치하기|$map:02000161$ 깊숙이 사라진 토끼를 처치하고 $item:39000026$ 찾기

10002361-null-NA.name: Clock Tower Pandemonium
10002361-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000871$ asked you to retrieve the $item:39000026$, which was stolen by a giant rabbit. Defeat the monsters in the $map:02000161$ while you hunt down that rabbit.
10002361-null-NA.manual: Defeat monsters in the $map:02000161$|Defeat the rabbit deep within $map:02000161$ and retrieve the $item:39000026$

10002362-null-.name: 혼돈의 시간
10002362-null-.desc: $npc:11000871$$pp:는,은$ 설계도에 나와 있는 시계탑 지하의 중추부를 찾아 가겠다며 $npc:11000870$에게 이 소식을 전해 달라고 한다.

10002362-null-NA.name: Dazed and Confused
10002362-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000871$ headed for the control room in the basement. Relay the news to $npc:11000870$.

10002370-null-.name: Cries of the Forest
10002370-null-.desc:
$map:02000017$'s $npc:11000350$ said that there have been cries coming from the cherry blossom forest and asked me to look into it.
Let's go to $map:02000017$'s eastern cherry blossom forest to investigate.
10002370-null-.complete: Investigate the cries coming from $map:02000017$'s eastern cherry blossom regions

10002371-null-.name: Dungeon: Broken Peace
10002371-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:21001001$ 
(Entrance: $map:2000017$)
Party Size (4 players)

$npc:11000499$ at $map:02000017$'s eastern cherry blossom forest asked me to save the Boroboro trapped inside the thorny vines. I'm still unsure as to what kinds of dangerous threats await inside, so let's tread with caution. It's time to gather up some companions to go to $map:02000290$, and save $npc:11000499$'s friends.
10002371-null-.manual: Save the Boroboro from the thorny vines in $map:02000290$

10002380-null-.name: Dungeon: Wicked Old Tree
10002380-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:21001001$ 
(Entrance: $map:2000017$)
Party Size (4 players)

$npc:11000499$ heard from friends at $map:02000017$'s pink Cherry Blossom Forest that $npc:11000751$, who was under the protection of the Boroboro, was taken by $npc:24000409$ and imprisoned in giant thorny vines. He'd been tasked with rescuing the princess...
Return to $map:02000290$ and defeat $npc:24000409$ so $npc:11000751$ may come back safely.

10002390-null-.name: Dungeon: All the King's Treasure
10002390-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:21005001$ 
(Entrance: $map:2000083$)
Party Size (4 players)

$map:02000083$'s $npc:11000101$ has asked to join forces to avenge $npc:11000503$, and has talked at great length of the king's treasure chest located in the deepest parts of $map:02000251$.
Since it doesn't inspire confidence to see one believe that words are all the strength one needs, it seems going to $map:02000251$ with more skilled friends than $npc:11000101$ is the better option.
10002390-null-.manual: Open the king's treasure chest in $map:02000251$

10002400-null-.name: Dungeon: Unacquainted with Death
10002400-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:21003001$ 
(Entrance: $map:3000014$)
Party Size (4 players)

10002430-null-.name: Dungeon: With Anos

10002440-null-.name: Maintaining Composure
10002440-null-.desc: $npc:11000119$ of $map:02000001$ has asked me to remember that the strength of the darkness threatening the world has increased along with my own. He said to stay humble... There are still many places in the world where Defenders and unsung heroes are battling the Demon King's darkness. I will find and assist them.

10002441-null-.name: The Qualifications of a Hero
10002441-null-.desc: $npc:11000076$ of $map:02000146$ has accepted me as a hero and informed me of my duty to stand up for this world. As $npc:11000076$ has requested I take on more difficult work, I've decided to meet $npc:11000266$ and $npc:11000009$ at $map:02000146$ and help them.
10002441-null-.manual: Help $npc:11000266$ and complete the story [City Threat]|Help $npc:11000009$ and complete the story [Curse of the Vayar Mountains]

10002442-null-.name: The Weight of a Hero
10002442-null-.desc: $map:02000146$'s $npc:11000076$ commanded me to meet $npc:11000007$ at $map:02000146$ and assist the Henesys Green Hood Vigilantes' guard activity.
10002442-null-.manual: Help $npc:11000007$ and complete the story [Demon's Servant ]

10002450-null-.name: 파괴의 법칙
10002450-null-.desc:

$map:02000145$에 자주 출몰하는 $npc:23000054$$pp:를,을$ 처치하고 $item:30000280$$pp:를,을$ $npc:11000065$에게 가지고 가자.

10002450-null-NA.name: The Outlaws of Robotics
10002450-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000266$ of $map:02000146$ sent an urgent request for help to $npc:11000065$. Apparently a giant robot is attacking the city.

Defeat $npcName:23000054$ at the $map:02000145$ and bring its $item:30000280$ to $npc:11000065$.

10002451-null-.name: 던전 : 빛을 잃은 도시
10002451-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20009001$ 
(입구 맵 : $map:02000164$)
파티권장 (4명)
노멀 모드에서만 퀘스트 수행이 가능합니다.

$npc:23100055$$pp:가,이$ 나타나서 날뛰는 바람에 $map:02000100$까지 전기가 끊어지게 생겼다며 걱정한다.

10002451-null-NA.name: City of Lost Lights
10002451-null-NA.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20009001$ 
Entrance: $map:02000164$
Party Size: 4 players
This quest is only available on normal difficulty.

$npc:11000065$ is worried about the $npc:23100055$ that has taken position on the $map:02000099$, where it can cut power to the city. Defeat the robot and restore power to the utility tower.

10002452-null-.name: 방심은 금물
10002452-null-.desc: $map:02000100$$pp:와,과$ $map:02000270$ 지역 간 갈등이 심각한 것 같다. $map:02000146$$pp2:로,으로$ 돌아가서 $npc:11000266$에게 $npc:11000065$의 당부를 전해주자.

10002452-null-NA.name: Tightening Security
10002452-null-NA.desc: It seems the divide between $map:02000100$ and $map:02000270$ is quite severe. Return to the $map:02000146$ and deliver $npc:11000065$'s request to $npc:11000266$.

10002460-null-.name: The Sacred Feather
10002460-null-.desc: $map:02000146$'s $npc:11000009$ has stated that assistance is required to unravel the curse and grief at the Vayar Mountains, and that I should help $npc:11000039$ prepare the offerings for the service. I should be able to acquire $item:30000281$ from either $npc:23000019$ or $npc:23000020$.

10002461-null-.name: Dungeon: The Sacred Rock
10002461-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20002001$ 
(Entrance: $map:02000148$)
Party Size (4 players)
Quest possible only on Normal Mode.

$npc:11000009$ of $map:02000146$ has asked me to defeat the $npc:23100100$ and anything protecting $map:02000313$. I'm also to retrieve the $item:30000282$ and bring it to $npc:11000302$.
With reliable comrades, I should have no problem retrieving the $item:30000282$ in $map:02000313$.

10002462-null-.name: Noble Beginnings
10002462-null-.desc: Expressing great trust and faith in $npc:11000009$, the son of $npc:11000134$, the chief of the Murpagos tribe, $npc:11000302$, has requested a relay of gratitude for retrieving the required offerings.

10002470-null-.name: Origins of Evil
10002470-null-.desc: $npc:11000007$ of $map:02000146$ believes that the powerful dark energy of the Devilyns in $map:02000115$ comes from the giant horns on their heads. I've been tasked with defeating them and retrieving $item:30000283$.

10002471-null-.name: Dungeon: Souls Awoken from Darkness
10002471-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20006001$ 
(Entrance: $map:02000146$)
Party Size (4 players)
Quest possible only on Normal Mode.

$npc:11000007$ of $map:02000146$ has expressed that the source of the darkness within $item:30000283$ was created by $npc:23100007$ by waking up spirits sleeping in darkness.
Let's get to $map:02000356$, defeat $npc:23100007$, destroy the spirit stone used to wake the sleeping spirits and report the situation to $npc:11000015$ of $map:02000076$.
10002471-null-.manual: (Boss) Defeat $npc:23100007$ at $map:02000356$|Destroy the Spirit Stone at $map:02000213$

10002472-null-.name: This Is Just the Beginning
10002472-null-.desc:
The Devilyns are merely the tail end of the Shadow Forces, or so says $npc:11000015$. It is of vital importance to remove the head from the Shadow Force's body. In order to accomplish this, it is primal that all of Maple World's Defenders and heroes trust and rely on one another.
Let's return to $map:02000146$ and deliver the message of $npc:11000015$ to $npc:11000007$.

10002480-null-.name: 책 벌레, 아폴로
10002480-null-.desc:
$npc:11000033$$pp:는,은$  [$item:39000011$] 책이 없어졌다고 말하며 $npc:11000604$$pp:가,이가$ 가지고 갔을 거라고 짐작하며 책을 돌려받아 가지고 오라고 말한다.
$map:02000023$의 $map:02000109$에서 $npc:11000604$$pp:를,을$ 찾아보자.

10002480-null-NA.name: Apollo the Bookworm
10002480-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000033$ believes that $npc:11000604$ has taken his book, [$item:39000011$], and requested that you retrieve it.

Search for $npc:11000604$ at $map:02000023$'s $map:02000109$.

10002481-null-.name: 독이 든 발톱
10002481-null-.desc: $npc:11000604$$pp:는,은$ $item:39000011$에 나와있는 내용 중 $npc:22000038$에 대한 내용이 진짜인지 확인해 보고 싶다며, $map:02000089$$pp2:로,으로$ 가서 $item:30000189$$pp:를,을$ 구해 오라고 한다.

10002481-null-NA.name: Claws-on Research
10002481-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000604$ is willing to return $item:39000011$'s in exchange for some help with some hands-on-research.

All you need to do is harvest a $item:30000189$ from a $npc:22000038$ in $map:02000089$.

10002482-null-.name: 엘리니아의 괴수
10002482-null-.desc: $npc:11000604$$pp:는,은$ 책을 마저 다 읽을 시간을 벌기 위해 일부러 $item:30000189$$pp:를,을$ 구해 오라고 한 것이었다며 약을 올렸다. $npc:11000604$$pp:가,이$ 얄밉기는 하지만 $item:39000011$$pp:를,을$ 기다리고 있을 $npc:11000033$$pp:를,을$ 생각하면 잘잘못을 따질 시간이 없다. $npc:11000604$에게서 $item:30000189$$pp:를,을$ 받아서 $map:02000023$$pp2:로,으로$ 돌아가자.

10002482-null-NA.name: Ellinia's Monster
10002482-null-NA.desc: It turns out that $npc:11000604$ only sent you off to find the $item:30000189$ to buy time to read his book. Well, there's no sense getting upset now. $npc:11000033$ waiting in $map:02000023$ for you to return his copy of $item:39000011$.

10002490-null-.name: 던전 : 마지막 기록
10002490-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20010001$ 
(입구 맵 : $map:02000067$)
파티권장 (4명)
노멀 모드에서만 퀘스트 수행이 가능합니다.

$npc:11000995$에게 실종된 빅토리아호의 선장은 아버지나 다름없는 분이라고 한다. 깊은 바다 한 가운데에서 흔적도 없이 사라져 버린 가족을 찾는 심정으로 $npc:11000995$$pp:는,은$ 빅토리아호 실종 사건의 진상을 밝히고 싶어하는 것 같다.
실종된 빅토리아호 선장과 똑같은 이름으로 스스로를 지칭하는 $npc:23100015$!!
과연 그 실체는 무엇일지, 그 녀석이 정말 $item:39000032$$pp:를,을$ 가지고 있는지 확인해 보자.

10002490-null-NA.name: Dungeon: Captain's Log
10002490-null-NA.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20010001$

Party Size: 4 players

$npcName:11000995$ wants to unravel the truth of what happened to the Victoria. His investigation has revealed that the leader of the undead pirates goes by the same name as the captain of the lost ship! He wants you to find out the truth about this so-called $npc:23100015$ as well as to retrieve $item:39000032$.

10002500-null-.name: Emergency Summons

10002502-null-.desc:

So, let's meet $npc:11000001$ in $map:02000076$.

10002503-null-.desc:

So, let's meet $npc:11000019$ in $map:02000062$.
10002503-null-.manual: Help $npc:11000019$ and complete the story [Shadow of the Ocean]

$npc:11000119$ ordered me to $map:02000142$ to help $npc:11000869$.
So, let's meet $npc:11000869$ in $map:02000142$.
10002504-null-.manual: Help $npc:11000869$ and complete the story [Shadow of Time]

10002510-null-.name: Find the Forest Spirit!
10002510-null-.desc: $npc:11000031$ says to defeat $npc:23000035$, $npc:23000017$, and $npc:23000047$, for they are absorbing all the $item:30000314$ which purifies the darkness and protects the forest. I must reclaim $item:30000314$.
10002510-null-.manual: (Boss) Defeat the giant monster at $map:02000023$ forest and reclaim $item:30000314$

10002511-null-.name: Dungeon: Forest of Lost Light
10002511-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20005001$ 
(Entrance: $map:02000090$)
Party Size (4 players)

10002511-null-.manual: Receive $item:30000315$ from $npc:11000031$|Unveil the light of the forest at $map:02000315$

10002520-null-.name: Strength of a Green Earth
10002520-null-.desc: $npc:11000001$ says to defeat $npc:22000322$, $npc:22000001$, and $npc:22000024$, for they are absorbing all the $item:30000316$ which purifies and protects the green meadows. I must reclaim $item:30000316$.
10002520-null-.manual: (Elite) Defeat monsters in the $map:02000076$ region and reclaim $item:30000316$

10002521-null-.name: Dungeon: Life, Purification, and Peace
10002521-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20003001$
(Entrance: $map:02000009$)
Party Size (4 players)
Quest possible only on Normal Mode.

After handing me a $item:30000317$ covered in $item:30000316$, $npc:11000001$ told me to go to $map:02000316$ and cover the baby Griffins with $item:30000317$ so that they may be born in their sacred form.
10002521-null-.manual: Receive $item:30000317$ from $npc:11000001$|Hatch fresh young griffins at $map:02000316$

10002530-null-.name: Ghostly Pirate Colony
10002530-null-.desc:
$npc:11000019$ has requested help in retrieving $item:30000318$ and defeating the pirates occupying both $map:02000063$ and $map:02000067$.
By meeting $npc:11000981$ at the marina in $map:02000062$ and riding the Marcos to $map:02000183$, I should be able to move quickly.
10002530-null-.manual: Defeat the pirates at $map:02000063$ and $map:02000067$ and find $item:30000318$

10002531-null-.name: Dungeon: Death's Path
10002531-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20010001$ 
(Entrance: $map:02000067$)
Party Size (4 players)
Quest possible only on Normal Mode.

$npc:11000995$ deciphered the coded message written by the captain of the Victoria and stolen from the pirates.
The captain's message stated that he left something in the treasure chest at the pirates' fortress...!
Let's go to $map:02000318$ and see if the message is right about the treasure chest!
10002531-null-.manual: Open the Footballfish treasure chest in $map:02000318$|Find clues left by the captain of the Victoria

10002532-null-.name: Chasing Victoria
10002532-null-.desc:
$npc:11000995$, having checked the last coordinates of the Victoria, believes that there is something unidentifiable near the strait and has requested the dispatch of a coastal exploration team.
$npc:11000982$ is preparing a boat at $map:02000183$, so I must quickly return to the $map:02000068$ of $map:02000062$ and tell $npc:11000019$ the news!

10002540-null-.name: Dungeon: Get to the Gear
10002540-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20011001$
(Entrance: $map:02000142$)
Party Size (4 players)
Quest possible only on Normal Mode.

Worried about the safety of $npc:11000871$, who entered $map:02000357$ of their own accord, $npc:11000869$ has requested the gear at $map:02000357$ be repaired, and that $npc:11000871$ be recovered.
Let's go into the $map:02000357$ through the entrance at the top of the clock tower!

10002550-null-.name: 몽실몽실 분홍양
10002550-null-.desc:
$npc:11000246$$pp:는,은$ $npc:11001013$에게 자신이 이사를 가기 전에 $item:30000328$$pp:를,을$ 데리고 집으로 놀러 오라고 전해 달라는 부탁을 했다.
$map:02000002$에서 $npc:11001013$$pp:를,을$ 찾아보자.

10002550-null-NA.name: Baa Baa Pink Sheep
10002550-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000246$ wants you to ask $npc:11001013$ to visit with her $item:30000328$. He's moving soon and wants to hang out one last time. Those sheep must be pretty darn adorable!
Look for $npc:11001013$ in $map:02000002$.

10002551-null-.name: 알퐁달퐁 목장으로
10002551-null-.desc:
$npc:11001013$$pp:는,은$ 여행을 떠나기 전 $item:30000328$$pp:를,을$ $map:52000002$에 맡겨두고 갔었다며, $item:30000328$$pp:를,을$ 데리고 와 달라고 부탁했다.
$map:02000002$에 있는 $map:52000002$$pp:를,을$ 찾아가서 $item:30000328$$pp:를,을$ 데리고 오자.

10002551-null-NA.name: To Baaalmy Farm
10002551-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11001013$ left her $item:30000328$ at $map:52000002$ before her trip and has asked you to get it while she tracks down that comic book. How hard can it be to wrangle one cute, little sheep?
You should go to $map:52000002$ in $map:02000002$ and bring back the $item:30000328$.

10002560-null-.name: 구하라, 핑크램!
10002560-null-.desc:
$npc:11000833$$pp:는,은$ 늑대들이 $map:52000002$$pp:를,을$ 습격하는 바람에 울타리도 부서지고 $item:30000328$도 물고 가 버렸다며 울먹였다.
$map:52000002$$pp2:로,으로$ 들어가서 $item:30000328$$pp:를,을$ 잡아간 늑대를 찾아 혼내주고, $item:30000328$도 무사히 구해오자.

10002560-null-NA.name: Save the Pastures!
10002560-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000833$ is in tears, because wolves broke through the fence into $map:52000002$ and ran off with $npc:11001013[gender:1]$'s $item:30000328$. You've got to go to $map:52000002$ fast and chase off those wolves before something bad happens to it.

10002570-null-.name: Dungeon: An Explorer's Curiosity
10002570-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20001001$
(Entrance: $map:02000183$)
Party Size (4 players)
Quest possible only on Normal Mode.

$npc:11000782$ at $map:02000183$ said that if he were a few years younger, he would have gone to $map:02000321$ and defeated $npc:23100006$ multiple times already, but is pressuring me to fight $npc:23100006$ instead.
Although the pressure is not getting to me, it may still be a challenge worth taking on.

10002571-null-.name: Legendary Tale
10002571-null-.desc: $npc:11000782$ from $map:02000183$ is attempting to boast to $npc:11001064$, an adventurer on dispatch from the Adventurer's Guild, about an experience at $map:02000353$.

10002572-null-.name: Dungeon: An Adventurer's Curiosity
10002572-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20001001$
(Entrance: $map:02000183$)
Party Size (4 players)
Quest possible only on Normal Mode.

Unwilling to accept an adventurer with no proof of courage, $npc:11001064$ at $map:02000183$ has said to return after gaining a perfect understanding of $npc:23100006$.

10002620-null-.name: Courageous & Friendly
10002620-null-.desc:
$npc:11000136$ of $map:02000051$ spoke about $map:02000325$, where $npc:21800006$, through ancient spirit sorcery, has been directly fighting and judging the skills of challengers through the spirits monsters.
Let's go to $map:02000217$ and meet $npc:11000289$ to find out more about $map:02000325$.

10002621-null-.name: Dungeon: A New Challenge
10002621-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:25000001$
(Entrance: $map:2000217$)

$npc:11000289$ took the challenge at $map:02000325$, but couldn't even pass the first test. He assured me that until he passes all the tests he won't give up, and will continue to train for as long as it takes. 
He also proposed a bet in regards to whoever can pass the first test at $map:02000325$ and meet $npc:21800006$.
If there isn't a good reason to avoid it, then it's not such a bad idea to take up the challenge at $map:02000325$.

10002622-null-.name: Dungeon: Brave Spirit
10002622-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:25000001$
(Entrance: $map:2000217$)

$npc:11000675$ of $map:02000217$ advised me not to be lazy with training at $map:02000325$. I need to show everybody my spirit is brave and earn their recognition.

10002630-null-.name: Warm Encouragement
10002630-null-.desc:
$npc:11001177$, standing watch at the vigilante guard post at $map:2000057$, couldn't hide their excitement when speaking of $npc:11000015$. $npc:11000015$'s role is to personally check the guard posts near the $map:2000076$ region with the supply corps as a way of encouraging them. 
Since the guards can't afford to be negligent in their duties, $npcName:11001177$ has requested that I deliver $item:30000412$ to the supply soldier who has gone to $map:2000091$.

10002631-null-.name: Dungeon: Enemy Beyond the Palace
10002631-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:25003001$ 
(Entrance: $map:2000091$)

$npc:11000959$ of $map:2000091$ requested my help in protecting the watchtower beyond the palace walls, as wild pigs are after the emergency rations located inside. $npc:11000015$ and the supply corps are doing their best in this emergency situation and need my help. 
Let's go to $map:02000334$ to defeat the pigs and protect the watchtower!
10002631-null-.manual: Defeat the leader of the pig herd at $map:02000334$

10002640-null-.name: Dungeon: Revenge Gone Wrong
10002640-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:02000334$ 
(Entrance: $map:2000091$)

$npc:11001178$ is hiding in the lower region of $map:2000091$!
He angrily confirmed that $npc:24001205$, the leader of the pigs attacking $map:02000334$, originally escaped from his pig farm and totally ruined the place when it returned to attack on more than one occasion. $npc:11001178$ warned that $npc:24001205$ won't give up until all the rations inside the watchtower are taken. He said that even as he speaks, $npc:24001205$ is probably gathering more pigs in order to cause more chaos.
Could $npc:11001178$'s words be true? Would the pigs I assumed were utterly defeated attack the palace walls again? 
Let's return to $map:02000334$ and check out the situation!
10002640-null-.manual: Defeat $npc:24001205$, the leader of the pig herd, at $map:02000334$

10002650-null-.name: Strange Ones
10002650-null-.desc:
In the middle of $map:2000064$ there are some fairly odd people.
$map:2000064$ $npc:11000172$ suspects that these unidentified people are the strangers who entered through $map:2000062$ a few days ago.
Who are they?
Where are they from?
Why have they come here?
Let's meet the strange people face to face!

10002660-null-.name: Well-deserved Me Time
10002660-null-.desc: $npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating! She says you look exhausted, and suggests you take a spa day and get refreshed! You are feeling pretty tired. Maybe you should take her suggestion? If you are not so lucky as to have a tub or massage chair to utilize in your own home, why not wander into someone else's?
10002660-null-.manual: Take a bubble bath in a $item:50400036$ |Wash your feet in a $item:50400091$ |Receive a massage in a $item:50400037$

10002661-null-.name: The Idiot Box
10002661-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating!
Having heard that watching TV makes you stupid, she asks you for help finding the truth of this myth.

Does TV really make you stupid? You should go find out! What's the worst that could happen?

10002662-null-.name: Befriending a Feline
10002662-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating!
Spurned by the stray cats of $map:02000064$, she asks you to see if a $item:50400004$ will enhance her chances at feline companionship.

Well, anything for friendship! it looks like it's time to start knocking on doors until you find a house with a $item:50400004$, and a cat to play with.
10002662-null-.manual: Play with a cat in a $item:50400004$

10002663-null-.name: Raise the Roof
10002663-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating! She heard there's a house around here decorated like a dance club. She has tasked you with finding one such party-worthy house so she can get her groove on.

Look around for a house with the requested lighting conditions!

10002664-null-.name: Master of the Arcade
10002664-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating!
In the hopes of making new friends, she seeks the approval of local video game enthusiasts. $npcName:11001180$ asks you to try out various arcade games and find one that's not too difficult to play, so that she does not embarrass herself.

Time to go on a video game hunt!

10002665-null-.name: You've Got it Maid
10002665-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating! She is considering work as a maid in the hopes of learning more directly about the culture of Victoria Island.

$npcName:11001180$ has tasked you with performing various house chores, and reporting back as to how difficult a task it was. Nobody likes chores, but perhaps you can take one for the team.

Whether in your own house, or helping out at a friends, go take care of some chores!

10002666-null-.name: Healthy Habit #2
10002666-null-.desc: $npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating! Noticing the queasy look on your face, she advised you to seek out a toilet for immediate release. Come to think of it, when was the last time you relieved yourself? Perhaps you should take care of business now, before something regretable happens.
10002666-null-.manual: Use $item:50400054$ to take care of business

10002667-null-.name: The Odiferous Adventurer
10002667-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating!
Of particular note, is your profound odor! Perhaps you should take a break from adventuring and spend some time washing up?

At this point, any sink and shower should do.
10002667-null-.manual: Use $item:50400053$ to wash your face |Use $item:50400035$ to take a shower

10002668-null-.name: Think Cool
10002668-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating! Having heard of a wonderful device known as a "refrigerator," she has asked you to go and see if it works as well at keeping things cold as she has been told.

Find a home with the recommended brand of refrigerator, and pop your head inside!

10002669-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating!
Her latest infatuation is with the world of high-tech exercise equipment. Are these devices really better than exercising the old-fashioned way? Looks like it's up to you to find out!

Go find a $item:50400096$ and test it out!

Go forth and break stuff, in the name of stress relief!

10002690-null-.name: Earn Your Wings
10002690-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating!
Rumor has it, that if you free a fellow adventurer from under a tombstone, you can grow a pair of heavenly wings!

There's nothing wrong with doing a good deed in the name of wicked cool accessories!
10002690-null-.manual: Break other people's tombstones to save them from the clutches of death

10002691-null-.desc:
