10002697-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating!
For example, it's home to $map:2000033$, a cozy little spot to put your feet up and relax.

$npc:11001180$ says you should swing by, sit down, and take a load off. Why not? You can't spend every moment of the day saving the world.
10002697-null-.manual: Sit and relax at $map:2000033$ for 300 seconds

10002698-null-.name: A Wonderful Vacation
10002698-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating!
Sensing your growing weariness, she tells you to take a vacation at  $map:2000171$ in $map:2000178$, one of the finest resorts Maple World has to offer.

It's been a while since you took a break from smacking monsters and saving villages, what could a little vacation hurt?
10002698-null-.manual: Sit and relax at $map:2000178$ for 300 seconds

10002699-null-.name: Adventures in Literacy: A Griffin's Adventure
10002699-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating!
Having heard great things about the best-selling book "$item:39000001$," she asks you to procure her a copy. 

It sounds like such a sweet story. You should begin your book-search at $map:2000031$!

10002700-null-.name: Reduce, Reuse, Dismantle
10002700-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating! She suggests you dismantle any unneeded equipment to receive various useful materials. 

No sense letting that hideous outfit from 10 levels ago clog up your inventory! Obliterate it into scraps, and pretend it never existed!

10002701-null-.name: An Eventful Day
10002701-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating!
Having heard about the exciting events put on by the famous $npc:11000168$ has pressured you into participating.

She hasn't specified which... $map:61000002$, $map:61000001$, $map:61000006$, any of his events should do. Pick one, and go for first place!

10002702-null-.name: Furry-tailed Friends
10002702-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating, but above all she treasures friendship. As one of her friends, it would mean the world to $npcName:11001180$ if you got along with her oldest friend in Victoria Island, $npcName:11000711$. 

$npcName:11000711$ can be found near the taxi stop in $map:02000064$. Stop by and say hello!

10002703-null-.name: Dancing in the Dirt
10002703-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating!
Having heard rumors of mysteriously quaking patches of earth in $map:02000118$ she has asked you to investigate.

Well, you'd better drop everything to go stare at the dirt near $npc:11001310$ in $map:02000118$ for signs of movement.
10002703-null-.manual: Locate and investigate the shaking earth in $map:02000118$

10002704-null-.desc:

Eager to read something titled "$item:39000015$," but with no idea where to find it, she has once again tasked you with something any reasonably person would take care of themselves: book-shopping.

10002712-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating!
