You should try talking with $npc:11000325$ at $map:2000001$.

10002713-null-.name: Adventures in Literacy: Behind Bars
10002713-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$ finds everything about Maple World fascinating!
Eager to learn more about prison, she asks you to bring her a copy of "$item:39000009$." 

You should talk to the guards at $map:2000124$!

10002721-null-.name: Before Darkness Blooms
10002721-null-.desc:
$npcName:11000037$ of $map:2000023$ has spoken of the Havi monsters lurking around the shadow doors at Victoria Island.
The $item:30000435$, carrying a powerful dark energy, provide the Havi monsters the ability to linger past death as $item:30000435$ survives to bare fruit.
Let's defeat the powerful Havi monsters lurking around the shadow doors. They may be carrying $item:30000435$. I must collect it.
10002721-null-.manual: Defeat monsters of level 26 and above near the shadow door and collect $item:30000435$

10002730-null-.name: Darkness Returned
10002730-null-.desc:
$map:2000350$ is a branch of the giant darkness that has been discovered in $map:2000048$, and $npc:11000031$ of $map:2000023$ has requested assistance in uprooting it.
Let's meet $npc:11001228$ in $map:2000048$.

10002731-null-.name: Dungeon: A Meaningful First Challenge
10002731-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:25008001$
(Entrance: $map:2000048$)

$npc:11001228$, who I came across at the entrance of $map:2000350$ of $map:2000048$, has explained that $map:2000350$ is a branch grown from the Seed of Darkness, and that it functions as a conduit for which darkness spreads.
Though not an easy task, everyone must work together to fight this giant darkness, otherwise the world will belong to the Demon King.
In order to fill the world's darkness with light, we must be brave and push onward.
10002731-null-.manual: Remove the first darkness at $map:2000350$ and pass

10002740-null-.name: [Dungeon] Attacking the Darkness
10002740-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:25008001$
(Entrance: $map:2000048$)

$npcName:11001241$ is unable to fulfill her duty of purifying the $map:2000350$ due to Havi poisoning. She doesn't think you have what it takes to do her job, and challenges you to survivng ten waves in
the $map:2000350$.

10002750-null-.name: Flying Blind
10002750-null-.desc:
$npcName:11000407$, who lives in $map:2000306$ of $map:2000133$, heard that some vagabond in the Land of Darkness saw $npcName:11000064$ in $map:3000103$, and has requested confirmation.
I can get to the Land of Darkness's $map:3000103$ through the shadow door in $map:2000146$.
10002750-null-.complete: Go to $map:3000103$ the in Land of Darkness and find $npcName:11000064$

10002751-null-.name: Dungeon: Birth of the Demon
10002751-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:21013001$
(Entrance: $map:3000103$)
Party Size (4 players)
Quest possible only on Normal Mode.

$npc:11001238$, protector of the Land of Darkness's $map:3000103$, recalls seeing $npcName:11000064$ jump into $map:2000349$.
Is $npcName:11000064$ safe? I should hurry inside $map:2000349$ and look for $npcName:11000064$...

10002752-null-.name: Reckless Life
10002752-null-.desc: After hearing what happened in $map:2000349$, $npcName:11000407$ of $map:2000306$ requested I go to $map:2000228$ at $map:2000146$, take $item:30000434$ to treat $npcName:11000064$'s injury, and then ask him why he went to $map:2000349$ alone.

10002760-null-.name: Forbidden Adventure
10002760-null-.desc:
The Boroboro Fairy $npcName:11001239$ is shaking in terror on one side of $map:2000103$!
Out of curiosity, she and other $map:2000023$ Fairies defied the chief's orders and left the village on an adventure to the Land of Darkness. During their journey, they came face-to-face with the witch who protects $map:3000103$, but she was the only one who managed to escape.
She wants her friends delivered from $map:3000103$...
Let's get to $map:3000103$ in the Land of Darkness and search for the Fairies with $npcName:11001239$.

At $map:3000103$ exists the Land of Darkness, which is connected to the $map:2000146$ shadow door.

10002761-null-.name: Dungeon: Tricky Witch
10002761-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:21013001$
(Entrance: $map:3000103$)
Party Size (4 players)
Quest possible only on Normal Mode.

$npcName:11001238$ in $map:3000103$ is smiling slyly, having lied to $npcName:11001239$ and the other Fairies about being able to find a shortcut home if they jumped into $map:2000349$.
Let's go into $map:2000349$ and save the Fairies before their souls are devoured by darkness.
10002761-null-.manual: Save all the Fairies at $map:2000349$ in the Land of Darkness's $map:3000103$
10002761-null-.complete: Meet $npcName:11001238$ at the Land of Darkness's $map:3000103$

10002762-null-.name: Dungeon: Curious Witch
10002762-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:21013001$
(Entrance: $map:3000103$)
Party Size (4 players)
Quest possible only on Normal Mode.

$npcName:11001238$ of $map:3000103$ says if I find out who the Demon King's new son born in $map:2000349$ is, she will give me a valuable treasure chest.
Although I am curious about the witch's treasure chest, finding out about the Demon King's new son is a challenge worth doing whether anything comes from it or not.
10002762-null-.manual: Defeat the Demon King's son at $map:2000349$ in the Land of Darkness's $map:3000103$
10002762-null-.complete: Meet $npcName:11001238$ at the Land of Darkness's $map:3000103$

10002770-null-.name: Where Is He?
10002770-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001274$ is waiting in the grassy field behind the taxi stop at $map:2000064$!
Seems as though he is waiting on Bomar, a member of the Arikari Merchant Society...
Where is Bomar, anyway?
Shouldn't there be someone in the Arikari Merchant Society, located in $map:2000064$, who may know his whereabouts?

10002771-null-.name: Best Buds
10002771-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001180$, who has been looking around $map:2000064$ excitedly, is now reminiscing and listening to stories of his homeland, Karkara Island. Unfortunately, there hasn't been any news of Bomar... Could $npcName:11001181$, Bomar's closest friend within the Arikari Merchant Society, know of his whereabouts?
Let's go see!

10002772-null-.name: Secret Message
10002772-null-.desc: $npcName:11001181$ revealed that Bomar left a letter asking for the care of $npcName:11001274$ until he returned. The letter was delivered by $npcName:11000994$, who is in charge of all the minor chores in $map:2000062$. $npcName:11001181$ says I should ask $npcName:11000994$, for he may know of Bomar's whereabouts.

10002773-null-.name: Back to Home!
10002773-null-.desc:
$npcName:11000994$ of $map:2000062$ said that Bomar went on a boat to $map:2000183$ with $npc:11001276$.
$map:2000183$… Why would Bomar go all the way there with the inventors?
Going to $map:2000183$ to find Bomar and his company seems like the thing to do...but walking there won't be easy.
$npcName:11000994$ secretly gives boat rides to $map:2000183$. I should ask him for a favor...

10002840-null-.name: The Nightmare
10002840-null-.desc:
They who followed the ancient Lumieragons and protected the royals: the Moropapa!
$npc:11001314$'s granddaughter, $npcName:11001215$, shared that her grandfather has been suffering from a nightmare, where in the depths of Nazkar Temple a giant black dragon appears and the temple crumbles.
For $npcName:11001215$, who is shaking with anxiety, let's get into Nazkar Temple and explore $map:02010029$ to see if anything has happened.

10002841-null-.name: Dungeon: Secrets of Lubelisk
10002841-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:2010055$
(Entrance: $map:02010029$)
Party Size (10 players)

$npc:11001483$, hiding by the entrance to $map:02010055$, noted that $npcName:11001215$'s grandfather's nightmare may actually be true. $npc:11001483$ says that if I have the courage, I should into $map:02010055$ and find out what's going on.

10002860-null-.name: [Dungeon] Puri's gift.
10002860-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001228$ is a who fairy who is collecting havi fruit outside the $map:02000350$! She provides gifts and services for warriors fighting the corruption of the $map:02000350$. 

If you manage to make it deep enough inside, she'll give you a gift!

20001000-null-NA.name: DIY Cement
20001000-null-NA.desc: Hunt the $npcPlural:21000029$ gathered around the river in $map:02000017$ and acquire $itemPlural:20000055$ to use as building materials!
20001000-null-NA.manual: Hunt the $npcPlural:21000029$ at the river and acquire $itemPlural:20000055$

20001001-null-.name: 시멘트를 내손으로 직접!
20001001-null-.desc:
$map:02000017$의 $npc:11000350$ 옆에 있는 아궁이에서 $item:30000094$$pp:를,을$ 제작하자!
시멘트 제작에 필요한 $item:20000055$$pp:는,은$ $npc:21000029$$pp:를,을$ 사냥하면 또 구할 수 있다고 했으니 재료를 아낄 필요는 없을 것 같다.

20001001-null-NA.name: Handcrafted with Care!
20001001-null-NA.desc:
Craft $item:30000094$ at the furnace next to $npc:11000350$ of $map:02000017$!
If you don't have the $itemPlural:20000055$ you need to craft it, you can hunt $npcPlural:21000029$. Those things are everywhere, so you don't have to be sparing with the materials!
20001001-null-NA.manual: Get the $itemPlural:020000055$ from $npc:11000350$ and craft the $item:30000094$ in the furnace

20001030-null-.name: Puppy Rescue Strategy
20001030-null-.desc: Let's rescue $npc:11000355$'s puppy friends from around the meteor in $map:02000014$.

20001040-null-.name: 미니핌과의 숨바꼭질
20001040-null-.desc: $npc:11000358$$pp:를,을$ 위해 $map:02000110$ 곳곳에 있는 레버를 당겨 숨어있던 $npc:29000023$$pp:를,을$ 잡아 $item:30000097$$pp:를,을$ 가져다 주자.
20001040-null-.manual: 매립지 곳곳의 레버를 당겨 $npc:29000023$ 발견 후 $item:30000097$ 구하기

20001040-null-NA.name: Mini Pim Hide-and-Seek
20001040-null-NA.desc: All you need to do is pull all the levers in $map:02000110$, defeat the $npcPlural:29000023$, and deliver the $itemPlural:30000097$ to $npc:11000358$. Why not help a criminal come clean and start a new life?
20001040-null-NA.manual: Pull the levers at $map:02000110$ and retrieve $item:30000097$ from $npc:29000023$

20001050-null-.name: 소음 공해
20001050-null-.desc: $npc:11000359$$pp:를,을$ 위해 $map:02000086$의 몬스터들을 사냥하자. 그리하면 이곳에 산다는 $npc:11000359$의 아들이 좀 더 조용한 환경에서 지낼 수 있게 되지 않을까?

20001050-null-NA.name: Noise Pollution
20001050-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000359$ is really concerned about her son's beauty sleep. You should help them get a little peace and quiet by hunting monsters in $map:02000086$ for $npc:11000359$.

20001051-null-.name: 얼음과 용암사이
20001051-null-.desc: $map:02000086$의 $npc:11000359$$pp:를,을$ 위해 얼음팩을 용암 지역 오른편에 있는 $npc:11000360$에게 가져다 주자.

20001051-null-NA.name: Between a Hot and a Cold Place
20001051-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000359$ in $map:02000086$ is really worried about her son. She's asked you to take the ice pack to $npc:11000360$ just for safety's sake. You should be able to find him just to the right of the lava area.

20001052-null-.name: 용암과 얼음의 만남
20001052-null-.desc: $map:02000086$의 $npc:11000360$의 집 주변에 있는 용암 구멍을 얼음을 옮겨 막자.

20001052-null-NA.name: Lava, Meet Ice
20001052-null-NA.desc: The only way to save the house and bring the heat down is to block the lava holes. Maybe these ice blocks can cool the lava enough to solve both problems. Put ice in the lava hole near $npc:11000360$'s house in $map:02000086$.
20001052-null-NA.manual: Block the lava hole with ice

20001060-null-.name: 크래비 포획 작전
20001060-null-.desc:
$map:02000111$의 $npc:11000362$$pp:를,을$ 위해 $npc:29000033$$pp:를,을$ 해안의 함정으로 유인하자.
함정을 먼저 열어두고 내가 열어둔 함정으로 $npc:29000033$$pp:를,을$ 유인해오자!

20001060-null-NA.name: Crabby Capture
20001060-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000362$ in $map:02000111$ is really excited about cooking a tasty seafood meal. But, he needs lots of crab to do it. Why not help him lure $npcPlural:29000033$ into the traps at the beach?
20001060-null-NA.manual: Lure $npcPlural:29000033$ to the open traps and get $itemPlural:20000056$

20001061-null-.name: 발로 뛰는 홍보
20001061-null-.desc: $map:02000111$의 $map:02000085$ 포탈 앞 해변에 있는 관광객들에게 $item:30000140$$pp:를,을$ 홍보하자.

20001061-null-NA.name: Word-of-Mouth Advertising
20001061-null-NA.desc: So many people are missing out! Spread the word about $itemPlural:30000140$ and other culinary delights to all the tourists at the beach in front of the portal to $map:02000085$ in $map:02000111$.
20001061-null-NA.manual: Promote $itemPlural:30000140$ to the tourists at the beach

20001070-null-.name: 그 돼지는 용감했다
20001070-null-.desc: $map:02000088$에서 발견한 이 돼지는 대체 어디서 뛰어내린 걸까? 가까운 곳에 있는 타워에 올라가 보자.

20001070-null-NA.name: The Pig Takes Flight
20001070-null-NA.desc: The discovery of a pig's body amidst the wreckage of what seems to have been an aircraft has left you with questions that must be answered. Perhaps he jumped from above? Search the nearby tower in $map:02000088$.
20001070-null-NA.complete: Climb the tower at $map:02000088$ and read the pig's diary

20001090-null-.name: 길 막는 나무들
20001090-null-.desc: $map:02000017$의 $npc:11000368$$pp:를,을$ 위해 $npc:11000368$ 옆에서 $item:30000104$$pp:를,을$ 꺼낸 후,$map:02000017$ 길가 주변에 심어져 있는 묘목에 $item:30000104$$pp:를,을$ 뿌리자.
20001090-null-.manual: $map:02000017$ $npc:11000368$의 바구니에서 $item:30000104$ 꺼내기|$map:02000017$에서 길가에 있는 묘목에 묘약 뿌리기

20001090-null-NA.name: Wood Blocked
20001090-null-NA.desc: You've got to save the forest! Get some $item:30000104$ from the basket next to $npc:11000368$ of $map:02000017$, then spray it on the seedlings that are planted on the roads around $map:02000017$.
20001090-null-NA.manual: Get $item:30000104$ from $npc:11000368$'s basket |Spray $item:30000104$ on the seedlings along $map:02000017$

20001100-null-.name: 원료에 대하여
20001100-null-.desc: $map:02000145$에 있는 컴퓨터들 중 A-NRL에 저장된 데이터를 읽자.

20001100-null-NA.name: Unbiased Science
20001100-null-NA.desc: Copy data from $npc:11000369$, a computer in $map:02000145$.

20001101-null-.name: 성분 비율에 대하여
20001101-null-.desc: $map:02000145$에 있는 컴퓨터들 중 B-NRL에 저장된 데이터를 읽자.

20001101-null-NA.name: Composition Analysis
20001101-null-NA.desc: Copy data from $npc:11000370$, one of the computers in $map:02000145$.

20001102-null-.name: 활용에 대하여
20001102-null-.desc: $map:02000145$에 있는 컴퓨터들 중 C-NRL에 저장된 데이터를 읽자.

20001102-null-NA.name: Usage Simulations
20001102-null-NA.desc: Copy data from $npc:11000371$, a computer in $map:02000145$.

20001110-null-.name: 꺼지는 사랑
20001110-null-.desc: $map:02000087$의 $npc:11000376$$pp:가,이$ 설치한 하트 메시지$pp:를,을$ 찾아 꺼진 불은 없는지 검사하자.

20001110-null-NA.name: I Want to Believe
20001110-null-NA.desc: Do aliens walk among us? It's time to find out! Investigate the "messages" $npc:11000376$ left for them in $map:02000087$, and see if there's been any response!

20001120-null-NA.name: The Long Ascent
20001120-null-NA.desc: Speak with $npc:11000382$ at the top of $map:02000148$.

20001121-null-NA.name: Beginning the Climb
20001121-null-NA.desc: Speak with $npc:11000379$ at the top of $map:02000135$.

20001122-null-NA.name: Reaching the Summit
20001122-null-NA.desc: Speak with $npc:11000380$ at the top of $map:02000110$.

20001130-null-.name: Cure All Mandecassol
20001130-null-.desc: Let's go retrieve $item:20000057$ from near the $map:02000159$ entrance in $map:02000134$ for $npc:11000384$, who was injured in $map:02000135$.
20001130-null-.manual: Retrieve $item:20000057$ from near the $map:02000159$ of $map:02000134$ entrance

20001140-null-.name: Unexpected Capture
20001140-null-.desc: Let's clean the fruit basket for $npc:11000385$ of $map:02000088$.

20001150-null-.name: 나무도 친구가 필요해
20001150-null-.desc: $map:02000041$의 $npc:11000386$$pp:를,을$ 위해  $npc:11000386$ 남쪽에 있는 붉은 나무들을 옮겨 심어주자.

20001150-null-NA.name: Happy Little Trees
20001150-null-NA.desc: Hurum would be so much happier with friends. You should find some red trees south of $npc:11000386$ and replant them in $map:02000041$.
20001150-null-NA.manual: Find the red trees located south of $npc:11000386$ and replant them

20001160-null-.name: 몰카 촬영?
20001160-null-.desc:
$map:02000137$에서 만난 사생팬 $npc:11000387$$pp:를,을$ 위해 $npc:11000406$의 사진을 촬영하자.
공연장 왼쪽 구조물에 올라가 촬영하면 된다.
20001160-null-.manual: $npc:11000387$에게 $item:30000109$ 받기|공연장 왼쪽 구조물에 올라가서 $npc:11000406$ 사진 다각도 촬영하기

20001160-null-NA.name: Clandestine Photo Shoot
20001160-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000387$ is desperate for photos of $npcName:11000406$, the celebrity currently visiting $map:02000137$.

Sure, it may seem odd, but it's a victim-less crime. Help a lovesick girl out and take some photos with her totally inconspicuous $item:30000109$.
20001160-null-NA.manual: Get the $item:30000109$ from $npc:11000387$|Take photos of $npc:11000406$ from the structure near the stage

20001171-null-.name: Apple Commotion
20001171-null-.desc: Let's go pick the apples from the apple tree located on the road to $map:02000116$ from $map:02000115$.
20001171-null-.manual: Bring back $item:30000128$ from the apple tree in $map:02000115$

20001190-null-.name: 아티스트 vs 아티스트
20001190-null-.desc: $map:02000110$ 곳곳에 있는 버섯이 그려진 그래피티를 지우자.

20001190-null-NA.name: Artist vs. Artiste
20001190-null-NA.desc: Time to erase the ugly mushroom graffiti all over $map:02000110$. It's pretty unsightly, really. Who'd want to stare at a fungus all day?

20001191-null-.name: 예술적 복수
20001191-null-.desc: $map:02000086$에 있는 $npc:11000412$의 아지트 주변에 그래피티를 바꿔치기 하자.

20001191-null-NA.name: Artistic Vengeance
20001191-null-NA.desc: The best way to get rid of that terrible mushroom 'art' is to cover it over with something worth looking at. It'll be a piece of cake to replace the graffiti around $npc:11000412$'s hideout in $map:02000086$.
20001191-null-NA.manual: Replace the graffiti around $npc:11000412$'s house in $map:02000086$

20001200-null-.name: 뜨거운 꽃
20001200-null-.desc: $map:02000086$의 용암에서 자라는 $item:20000061$$pp:를,을$ 뽑아보자. 불타는 용암이 뜨거워도 무서워 말자!

20001200-null-NA.name: Petals of Fire
20001200-null-NA.desc:
If you're going to prove you're an adventurer worthy of respect, you'll have to uproot the $item:20000061$ growing in the lava of $map:02000086$.
A little lava's nothing you can't handle. After all, it's just a bit of blazing, liquid fire of doom.

20001201-null-.name: 뜨거운 전투
20001201-null-.desc:
$map:02000086$에 있는 용광로를 두드려 $npc:21000086$들을 깨운 후 $item:30000142$$pp:를,을$ 빼앗아 오자. 
용광로의 위치는 미니맵에서 확인하자.

20001201-null-NA.name: Fiery Combat
20001201-null-NA.desc:
Another opportunity to prove you're a real adventurer. Banging on the smelting furnace in $map:02000086$ is sure to annoy the $npc:21000086$. Wait for them to come find you and grab that $item:30000142$ fast!
You can double-check the location of the furnace on the mini map.
20001201-null-NA.manual: Bang on the smelting furnace in $map:02000086$ and steal $itemPlural:30000142$

20001210-null-NA.name: Crabby Sabotage
20001210-null-NA.desc: The economy in the area has been totally disrupted by $npc:11000362[gender:0]$'s new venture. Sabotage may not be very nice, but that $npc:11000420$ is definitely someone you don't want to cross. Use tubes to block $npc:11000362$'s $npc:29000033$ traps in $map:02000111$ before she gets mad at you.
20001210-null-NA.manual: Use tubes to block $npc:29000033$ traps on the beach

20001211-null-.name: 생선 도둑?
20001211-null-.desc: $npc:11000420$$pp:는,은$ $map:02000111$ 도심에 있는 $npc:21000101$들이 엄마의 가게에서 팔아야 하는 생선들을 훔쳐갔다고 의심하고 있다. $npc:21000101$들이 정말 생선 도둑이 맞는지 놈들을 처치해보자.

20001211-null-NA.name: Sticky Fish Fingers
20001211-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000420$ suspects that the $npcPlural:21000101$ in $map:02000111$ city center have stolen the fish her mother was trying to sell. You should help her confront them to find out if they really are the culprits.

20001220-null-.name: 숏다리의 꿈
20001220-null-.desc: $npc:11000471$$pp:는,은$ 작은 키가 불만이다. $map:02000136$$pp:를,을$ 돌아다니는 $npc:21099049$들 사이에 있는 영양제 상자에서 $item:20000064$$pp:를,을$ 훔쳐오자!

20001220-null-NA.name: Making it Big
20001220-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000471$ is tired of coming up short, and wants to make a change. Help him recover $itemPlural:20000064$ from the crates belonging to the $npcPlural:21099049$ in $map:02000136$!
20001220-null-NA.manual: Retrieve $itemPlural:20000064$  from the crates near the $npcPlural:21099049$

20001230-null-.name: 거미 박멸!
20001230-null-.desc: $npc:11000472$ 뒤에 있는 건물 틈으로 들어가 $npc:29000025$들을 잡아주자.

20001230-null-NA.name: The Itsy-Bitsy Spiders
20001230-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000472$, who is not the slightest bit afraid of spiders, was about to go and squish all of the $npcPlural:29000025$ infesting the crawl space behind him—that is, until you volunteered.

Well, get to stomping!
20001230-null-NA.manual: Enter the crawl space behind $npc:11000472$ and squish $npcPlural:29000025$

20001280-null-.name: Exciting Teleportation
20001280-null-.desc: TELI is a strange teleportation machine discovered in $map:02000163$. Why is this machine installed here in the midst of the chaos of other machines and robots?

20001281-null-.name: Back to Home
20001281-null-.desc: The teleportation device operates as normal. Now it's time to turn it on and get home.

20001290-null-.name: Melting Lava
20001290-null-.desc: The lava that needs to flow into $map:02000162$'s lava generator has hardened, and therefore the generator is not working. I should follow the path of the lava, locate the problem, and fix it.
20001290-null-.manual: Follow the lava, locate the blockage, and fix it

20001300-null-.name: 바위 틈을 비집고
20001300-null-.desc: $npc:11000599$$pp:는,은$ $map:02000045$의 동굴속에서 신발을 잃어버렸다. $npc:11000599$ 뒤에 보이는 막혀있는 동굴 입구 속으로 들어가, $item:30000180$$pp:를,을$ 구해주자.

20001300-null-NA.name: The Smooshed Shoe
20001300-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000599$ lost his shoe while spelunking at the $map:02000045$. Enter the cave system behind him and retrieve $item:30000180$.

20001320-null-.name: 강하게 키우자!
20001320-null-.desc: $npc:11000629$$pp:는,은$ $npc:11000630$$pp:가,이$ 아이들에게 날기 교육을 시키는 방식에 불만이 많다. $npc:11000628$들이 전부 무사히 건넜을리 없으니 $map:02000046$의 하단부에서 날기에 실패한 $npc:11000628$들을 도와주자.

20001320-null-NA.name: Flying Lessons
20001320-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000629$ is unhappy with how her husband, $npcName:11000630$, is teaching their children how to fly. She may have a point—$npcNamePlural:11000628$ who failed to make it across the $map:02000046$ are littering the canyon floor. Give them a helping hand.

20001330-null-.name: 인형의 비밀
20001330-null-.desc: $npc:11000372$의 연구 욕심은 끝이 없다. $map:02000145$에서 찾을 수 있는 $map:02000240$에서 소리의 정체를 파악한 후 증거물을 가져가자. $map:02000240$$pp:는,은$ $npc:11000372$ 아래에 위치해 있다.

20001330-null-NA.name: Things Best Left Buried
20001330-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000372$ speaks cryptically of a failed experiment, and an abomination that must be destroyed. Travel to $map:02000240$ in the $map:02000145$, destroy the failed experiment, and bring back proof of your deed.

The entrance to the $map:02000240$ is located below $npc:11000372$.
20001330-null-NA.manual: (Elite) Defeat $npc:22090166$ in the $map:02000240$ under the $map:02000145$ and obtain proof of your deed

20001340-null-.name: 불의 재료
20001340-null-.desc: $npc:11000541$$pp:는,은$ 툼바족들이 주민들의 집을 빼앗는 것에 진절머리가 난 것 같다. $map:02000048$ 곳곳에서 $item:30000198$$pp:를,을$ 획득하자.

20001340-null-NA.name: All Fired Up
20001340-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000541$ is furious at the Tumbai who have stolen her peoples' homes. She wants you to gather $itemPlural:30000198$s from the $map:02000048$.

20001341-null-.name: 활활 타올라라
20001341-null-.desc: $npc:11000541$$pp:는,은$ 놀랍게도 빼앗긴 집들을 모두 불태우자고 제안했다. $npc:11000541$에게 $item:30000198$$pp:를,을$ 받아서 $map:02000048$ 곳곳의 움막집들을 불태우자.

20001341-null-NA.name: Burn, Burn, Burn!
20001341-null-NA.desc: In a twist that nobody could have predicted, $npc:11000541$ has decided to burn down her whole village rather than let the T'oomba kick them out. Use the $item:30000198$ you gathered to burn down homes at the $map:02000048$.
20001341-null-NA.manual: Use $item:30000198$ to burn homes at the $map:02000048$

20001350-null-.name: No Contact
20001350-null-.desc: $npc:11000664$ wants to hack $map:02000162$'s antenna in order to see his girlfriend's text message log. Let's hunt the monsters in $map:02000162$ and acquire $item:30000035$ for $npc:11000664$.

20001351-null-.name: To Hack, or Not to Hack
20001351-null-.desc: Using $item:30000035$, $npc:11000594$ produced $item:30000040$. Let's go to $npc:11000666$ at the upper region of $map:02000162$ and attempt to hack.
20001351-null-.complete: Hack $npc:11000666$, located in the upper region of $map:02000162$

20001360-null-.name: 울부짖는 석상
20001360-null-.desc: 보름달이 뜨는 날의 밤이면, $map:02000051$ 서쪽 꼭대기에 위치한 늑대 석상이 울부짖는다는 소문이 있다. 소문의 주인공인 석상을 살펴보자.
20001360-null-.manual: $map:02000051$ 서쪽 꼭대기에 위치한 늑대 석상 조사하기

20001360-null-NA.name: The Howling Stone
20001360-null-NA.desc: Rumor has it that, on a full moon, the wolf statue in northwestern $map:02000051$ howls like a real wolf. You need to see this for yourself.
20001360-null-NA.manual: Watch the wolf statue in northwestern $map:02000051$

20001361-null-.name: 울음소리의 정체
20001361-null-.desc: $map:02000081$ 다락방에서 숨어있을 곳을 찾아, $npc:11000694$$pp:가,이$ 나타나길 기다리자.

20001361-null-NA.name: The Voice of the Statue
20001361-null-NA.desc: Find a place to hide within the $map:02000081$ attic and wait for $npcName:11000694$ to appear.
20001361-null-NA.manual: Hide in the $map:02000081$ attic and learn $npcName:11000694$'s secret

20001370-null-.name: A Habit of Three...
20001370-null-.desc: $npc:11000001$ has been so worried he hasn't been able to sleep ever since a man in black came by looking for $npc:11000502$, his son. Let's go ask $npc:11000101$ in $map:02000083$ about $npc:11000502$'s whereabouts.

20001372-null-.name: Big Dreams, Bigger Punishments
20001372-null-.desc: $npc:11000502$ is being chased...for it has been revealed that he stole the $item:30000016$ from the Darkstar. I'm going to look for those who robbed $npc:11000502$ at $map:02000141$ and see if I can't find the stolen $item:30000016$.
20001372-null-.complete: Find the culprit who stole the $item:30000016$ from $map:02000141$

20001373-null-.name: Dungeon: Black Market Den
20001373-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:21005001$ 
(Entrance: $map:2000083$)
Party Size (4 players)

$item:30000016$ can only be found in $map:02000241$. If I go down the stairs by the Golden Tower in $map:02000083$, there will be a emergency door that is connected to $map:02000241$!
I must keep in mind $npc:11000365$'s advice on gathering comrades and advancing in a group of 4 within $map:02000241$...
20001373-null-.manual: Go downstairs from $map:02000241$ and look for $item:30000016$

20001380-null-.name: 멈춰버린 멜로디
20001380-null-.desc:
$npc:11000890$$pp:는,은$ 최근 $map:02000095$에 아름답게 울려퍼지던 멜로디 소리가 들리지 않아 원인을 찾던 중 의심스러운 토템을 발견했다고 한다. 
수상한 토템을 제거하여, 정적이 흐르는 $map:02000095$에 아름다운 멜로디를 되찾아주자.

20001380-null-NA.name: Broken Melody
20001380-null-NA.desc: The beautiful music of $map:02000095$ has been silenced, and $npcName:11000890$ thinks that some strange totems are behind it. Remove the totems and restore music to $map:02000095$.
20001380-null-NA.manual: Remove the strange totems in the $map:02000095$

20001381-null-.name: 치치의 걱정거리
20001381-null-.desc:
수상한 토템은 모두 제거 되었다. 
$npc:11000890$$pp:는,은$ 이 사실을 $map:02000095$ 꼭대기에 있는 $npc:11000891$에게 전해달라고 부탁한다.

20001381-null-NA.name: Chechy's Plan
20001381-null-NA.desc: Now that the totems are gone, $npc:11000890$ wants you to tell her brother, $npc:11000891$. He can be found near the highest point at $map:02000095$.
20001381-null-NA.complete: Talk to $npc:11000891$ at the top of $map:02000095$

20001382-null-.name: 도난당한 풀피리
20001382-null-.desc: $npc:11000891$$pp:는,은$ 잠들어 버린 요정들을 깨우기 위해 필요한 $item:30000261$$pp:를,을$ 도난 당했다고 한다.  $npc:21000065$$pp:를,을$ 사냥하여, 도난당한 $item:30000261$$pp:를,을$ 찾아주자.

20001382-null-NA.name: Flute Felony
20001382-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000891$ says that he needs his $item:30000261$ to awaken the guardians of the fountain. Unfortunately, it was stolen by a $npc:21000065$. Get the $item:30000261$ back.
20001382-null-NA.complete: Talk to $npc:11000891$ at the top of $map:02000095$

20001383-null-.name: 음악은 사랑을 싣고
20001383-null-.desc: $npc:11000891$$pp:는,은$ 되찾아온  $item:30000261$$pp:를,을$ 연주하면, 멜로디 분수를 깨울 수 있는 세 명의 요정을 불러낼 수 있다고 한다.  $item:30000261$$pp:를,을$ 연주하여, 잠들어 있는 세 명의 수호 요정을 깨워보자.

20001383-null-NA.name: An Uplifting Tune
20001383-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000891$ has asked you to awaken the fairfolk guardians of the fountain by playing his $item:30000261$. You might as well give it a try.
20001383-null-NA.manual: Play the $item:30000261$ to summon the guardians
20001383-null-NA.complete: Talk to $npc:11000891$ at the top of $map:02000095$

20001384-null-.name: 진정한 파이터라면!
20001384-null-.desc: 여행자들을 위한 쉼터이자, 피추피추족의 문화적 특색이 살아있는 $map:02000095$에 위기가 찾아왔다. $map:02000095$$pp:를,을$ 위협하는 몬스터들을 사냥하자!

20001384-null-NA.name: A Call to Action
20001384-null-NA.desc: You found a notice calling for heroes to defend the $map:02000095$ from monsters. Fight for the future of the Picchu Picchu people!
20001384-null-NA.complete: Check the bulletin board in the $map:02000095$

20001420-null-.name: Memory Trace
20001420-null-.desc:
Once upon a time, $npc:11000929$ wrote a great book. But after spending a thousand years in Perion, $npc:11000929$ can't remember the location of the original manuscript. After tracing the ancient memory back, $npc:11000929$ found out the book is inside of an egg. The nest, decorated with multi-colored feathers, is located on the peak of the $map:02000267$.
The eggshell has hardened and solidified as time passed, so I'll need to hunt the $npc:21000255$ around the area and use its $item:30000268$ to hatch the egg.
Let's go to the $map:02000267$ to find the original manuscript of the book written by $npc:11000929$.
20001420-null-.manual: Use the $item:30000268$ to hatch the egg and find the $item:30000265$|Use the $item:30000268$ to hatch the egg and find the $item:30000266$|Use the $item:30000268$ to hatch the egg and find the $item:30000267$

20001421-null-.name: Sharing Is Caring
20001421-null-.desc:
$npc:11000929$ was practically leaping for joy after I managed to locate the original manuscript.
$npc:11000929$ claims the book will be a big hit as long as it gets published.
If that's the case, I might be able to make a lot of money if I show the manuscript to $npc:11000327$ in $map:02000001$. I should go speak with $npc:11000327$.

20001430-null-.name: I'm a Survivor
20001430-null-.desc: $npc:11000930$ was deeply hurt and disappointed by the humans when she lost her husband to the poachers. She has been raising her babies by herself in $map:02000267$. It's been difficult for $npc:11000930$ to hunt, as dangerous lava fountains have formed around the area recently. Let's help and bring $item:30000269$ so that she can feed her baby birds.
20001430-null-.manual: Hunt the $npc:29000041$ in the bushes and bring it to $npc:11000930$

20001440-null-.name: 구슬픈 울음소리
20001440-null-.desc:
앞을 볼 수 없지만, 대신 앞 날을 예측하고 바라볼 수 있는 $npc:11000931$. 얼마 전부터 사냥을 떠난 아내 앙카가 계속 꿈에서 나타난다고 한다. 
꿈 속에서 본 $map:02000267$의 용암지대로 가서 $item:30000270$$pp:를,을$ 찾은 후에, 양지바른 곳에 있는 제단에서 제사를 올려주자.

20001440-null-NA.name: Mournful Vision
20001440-null-NA.desc:
Although $npc:11000931$ is blind, he has the ability to see visions. He's been having recurring dreams about his mate, Anka, who never returned from her last hunt.

Go to the lava flows of $map:02000267$ and find $item:30000270$, then find a sunny place to lay her to rest.
20001440-null-NA.manual: Find $item:30000270$ in $map:02000267$ and lay her to rest at the altar

20001450-null-.name: 내겐 너무 골치 아픈 너
20001450-null-.desc:
오염된 산업폐수가 고여 있는 물길을 커닝시티 발전소의 강한 스파크가 관통하면서 도심 한 복판에 거대한 괴물이 돌아다니는 일이 발생했다. 
오염된 거대 돌연변이 $npc:23000013$$pp:는,은$ $map:02000100$ 전체를 병들게 할 지도 모른다.
도심 속에 나타난 $npc:23000013$$pp:를,을$ 처치하자.

20001450-null-NA.name: Life Finds a Way
20001450-null-NA.desc:
A huge monster wanders the city wreaking chaos after industrial waste enters the ecosystem and turns an unsuspecting frog into a thumping freak.

Defeat $npc:23000013$ in $map:02000084$ and put an end to the clomping croaker. It really won't change much in the grand scheme of things, but it sure will make one more day in this city a little more tolerable!

20001460-null-.name: Dungeon: Catastrophic Jealousy
20001460-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20012001$ 
(Entrance: $map:02000024$)
Party Size (4 players)
The quest is only available in Normal mode.

As the fallen angel Ariel spread the seeds of darkness, $npc:23100039$, the violent guard of the underground, became awakened.
$npc:23100039$ must be stopped, with it becoming increasingly more violent as it continues to absorb dark spirits.
It's time to defeat $npc:23100039$ captured in $map:02000312$.

20001470-null-.name: 무소식의 이유
20001470-null-.desc:
$npc:11000961$$pp:는,은$ $map:02000013$로 파견나간 대원들이 돌아올 때가 한참이 지났는데 아무런 소식도 없이 행방이 묘연해졌다고 말하며 걱정을 하고 있다. 
$map:02000013$$pp2:로,으로$ 가서 파견나간 자경단원들이 무사한지 행방을 조사해보자.

20001470-null-NA.name: The Long Silence
20001470-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000961$ hasn't heard back from the Green Hoods who were deployed to the $map:02000013$. Head out there and find out what happened to them.
20001470-null-NA.manual: Search for missing Green Hoods at the $map:02000013$

20001471-null-.name: 간절했던 손길
20001471-null-.desc:
나무 숲 사이로 몸을 숨기고 있는 $npc:11000962$.
$npc:11000961$$pp:가,이$ 말한 자경대원 중 한 명인듯 하다. 
$npc:11000962$$pp:는,은$ 갑작스럽게 무리를 지어 몰려온 몬스터들의 공격에 대응하지 못해 많은 사람들이 부상당했고, 파견 나올때 준비해왔던 구호물품도 모두 바닥이 나서 상황이 매우 좋지 않다고 한다.
가장 시급한 것은 부상당한 사람들을 치료해 주는 것! 
홀로 부상자들을 돌보고 있는 $npc:11000832$$pp:를,을$ 찾아가보자.

20001471-null-NA.name: Uphill Battle
20001471-null-NA.desc: You found one of the missing Green Hoods, $npc:11000962$. Her squad was ambushed by monsters and they don't have enough supplies to take care of the wounded. Find $npc:11000832$ and help take care of the injured Green Hoods.

20001480-null-.name: 임시 처방
20001480-null-.desc:
$npc:11000832$$pp:는,은$ 홀로 부상자들을 돌보느라, 눈코 뜰 새 없이 바쁘다. 갈수록 부상자들은 늘어가는데 이들을 치료 해줄 약이 바닥이 나 버리는 바람에 상황은 더 안 좋기만 하다.
부상당한 환자를 위한 비상약 제조법을 알고 있는 $npc:11000832$$pp:는,은$ 약 제조에 필요한 재료들을 구해달라고 부탁한다. 
근처에 있는 $npc:21000353$, $npc:21000003$$pp:를,을$ 사냥하여, $item:30000285$, $item:30000286$$pp:를,을$ 구해오자.

20001480-null-NA.name: Triage
20001480-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000832$ is swamped taking care of wounded Green Hoods. She needs to make more medicine, and it falls on you to gather the materials. Hunt $npcNamePlural:21000353$ and $npcNamePlural:21000003$ to acquire $itemPlural:30000285$ and $itemPlural:30000286$.

20001481-null-.name: 치료가 필요해
20001481-null-.desc:
$npc:11000963$에 의하면 부상당한 사람들이 치료도 받지 못한 채 거리에 쓰러져 있다고 한다. 안 그래도 치료제가 바닥이 나서 $npc:11000832$$pp:를,을$ 찾아가려고 했지만, 부상자들만 두고 갈 수는 없었다는 $npc:11000963$.
$npc:11000963$에게 받은 응급치료제를 가지고, 부상당한 사람들을 치료해주자.

20001481-null-NA.name: Rubbing It In
20001481-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000963$ gave you some medicine for the injured people below.

20001490-null-.name: 사수하라!
20001490-null-.desc:
$npc:11000972$$pp:는,은$ 급격하게 늘어나버린 몬스터의 공격을 홀로 힘겹게 막아내고 있다. 함께 파견나왔던 자경단원 대부분은 부상을 입었고, 비상 구호물품도 모두 바닥이 나버려서 버틸 수 있는 시간도 얼마 남지 않았다고 한다.
극한 상황에 처해 있음에도 불구하고 포기하지 않겠다고 당차게 말하는 $npc:11000972$.
$npc:11000972$$pp:를,을$ 도와 성채를 점령하고 있는 $npc:21000003$, $npc:21000353$, $npc:21000306$$pp:를,을$ 사냥하자.

20001490-null-NA.name: Holding the Fort
20001490-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000972$ is making a desperate stand against an army of monsters after the rest of her squad was injured and scattered. Alone and without supplies, she refuses to give up—help her by fighting off the hordes of $npcNamePlural:21000003$, $npcNamePlural:21000353$, and $npcNamePlural:21000306$ that are attacking the fortress.
20001490-null-NA.manual: Defeat $npcNamePlural:21000003$ at the $map:02000013$|Defeat $npcNamePlural:21000353$ at the $map:02000013$|Defeat $npcNamePlural:21000306$ at the $map:02000013$

20001500-null-.name: 아름답지 않은 소리
20001500-null-.desc:
$npc:11000741$$pp:는,은$ 새로운 음악 작곡에 한창 몰입 중이다. 밝은 장조의 음악을 만들어야 하는 까닭에 달콤한 향이 가득한 $map:02000186$으로 작업실까지 옮겼지만, 거리의 엉터리 악사들의 소음 때문에 폭발 직전의 상태가 되어버렸다.
창작의 고통으로 예민해질대로 예민해진 $npc:11000741$$pp:를,을$ 위해 $npc:21000278$, $npc:21000173$$pp:를,을$ 사냥하자.

20001500-null-NA.name: Cacophony
20001500-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000741$ has moved to a new studio in the remote $map:02000186$ in order to compose his magnum opus. Unfortunately, the locals are too noisy for him to concentrate. Beat up the $npcPlural:21000278$ and $npcPlural:21000173$ so that $npc:11000741$ can focus on writing real music.

20001510-null-.name: 살이 빠지지 않는 이유
20001510-null-.desc:
세상에서 자신이 가장 이쁘다고 생각하고 있는 $npc:11000973$! 
$npc:11000973$$pp:는,은$ 최근 직접 설계한 $item:30000288$ 대로 꾸준한 다이어트를 하고 있는데 살이 빠지지 않아 고민중이다. 
$npc:11000973$의 살이 빠지지 않는 이유를 알아내기 위해 $npc:11000974$$pp:를,을$ 찾아가보자.

20001510-null-NA.name: Diet Hard
20001510-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000973$ already knows that she's a beauty, but she wants to lose a little weight before swimsuit season begins! Her diet plan doesn't seem to be working, so drop by $npcName:11000974$ to get some nutrition advice.

20001511-null-.name: 다이어트의 적
20001511-null-.desc:
$item:30000288$$pp:를,을$ 보고 소스라치게 놀라는 $npc:11000974$. 일반 성인들도 하루에 이렇게 고열량 음식을, 그것도 많이 섭취하기는 힘들다고 한다. 
$npc:11000974$$pp:는,은$ $npc:11000973$의 잘못된 식습관과 다이어트 방법을 바로 잡아주기 위해 새로운 다이어트 음식을 만들어 주겠다고 한다.
$map:02000186$ 곳곳에 있는 $item:30000289$, $item:30000290$, $item:30000291$$pp:를,을$ 구해오자.
20001511-null-.manual: $npc:21000160$$pp:를,을$ 사냥하여 $item:30000289$ 구하기|황금색 사과나무에서 $item:30000290$ 따기|$map:02000186$ 곳곳에 있는 $item:30000291$ 찾아오기

20001511-null-NA.name: A Tasty Weight Loss Treat
20001511-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000974$ is horrified by $item:30000288$. She's going to work on some new dishes to help $npcName:11000973$ reach her weight loss goal. Gather some $itemPlural:30000289$, $itemPlural:30000290$, and $itemPlural:30000291$ from the $map:02000186$ for her.
20001511-null-NA.manual: Hunt $npcNamePlural:21000160$ for $itemPlural:30000289$|Pick $itemPlural:30000290$ from golden apple trees|Collect $itemPlural:30000291$ in the $map:02000186$

20001512-null-.name: 몸짱 프로젝트
20001512-null-.desc:
$npc:11000973$$pp:를,을$ 위해 정성스럽게 준비한 $item:30000292$$pp:가,이$ 완성되었다! 
음식이 식기 전에 서둘러 $npc:11000973$에게 $item:30000292$$pp:를,을$ 배달하자!

20001512-null-NA.name: Getting in Shape
20001512-null-NA.desc: $item:30000292$ is all packed, just for $npcName:11000973$! Deliver it to her before it gets cold.

20001520-null-.name: Finding Father
20001520-null-.complete: Meet Palmer the farmer in the cornfield at the Greeno Crossroads

20001530-null-.name: 뜨거운 수행
20001530-null-.desc:
아무도 그에 대한 정체를 알 수가 없다! 
자신을 '무림의 최강'이라 자처하는 $npc:11000976$!! 
생김새는 그럴 듯하나, 어찌 얘기를 하면 할수록 어딘가 텅텅… 
$npc:11000976$$pp:는,은$ 무림 최강 중의 최강을 가리는 대전에서 우승하기 위해 $item:30000294$$pp:를,을$ 구해가야 하는데, 부상을 입어 도저히 갈 수 없다고 말한다. 
겉은 너무 멀쩡해 보이는 $npc:11000976$.
속는 셈치고, $map:02000096$의 용암지대에서만 자라는 $item:30000294$$pp:를,을$ 구해오자!

20001530-null-NA.name: Scorching Skill
20001530-null-NA.desc:
$npcName:11000976$ claims to be one of the world's greatest martial artists. He looks the part, but the more you talk with him, the less convincing he is.

He's asked you to gather some $itemPlural:30000294$ so that he can participate in an important tournament. He seems harmless enough, so you might as well do it.

20001540-null-.name: 신이 내린 벌
20001540-null-.desc:
쿤쿤부족 제사장 $npcName:11000977$$pp:는,은$ 대지의 신께 올릴 777일간의 기도제를 준비하느라, 분주하게 움직이고 있다.
$npc:11000977$$pp:가,이$ 무사히 신께 제를 올릴 수 있도록, 필요한 제수용품을 가져다주자!
20001540-null-.manual: $npc:21000374$$pp:를,을$ 사냥하여 $item:30000295$ 구하기|$npc:21000377$$pp:를,을$ 사냥하여 $item:30000297$ 구하기|$npc:21000303$$pp:를,을$ 사냥하여 $item:30000296$ 구하기

20001540-null-NA.name: An Angry God
20001540-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000977$ is preparing for 777 days of prayer to the god of his people. Bring the items he needs to safely perform the ritual.

20001541-null-.name: 집결! 쿤쿤부족
20001541-null-.desc:
$npc:11000977$$pp:는,은$ 기도제에 올릴 모든 제수용품은 준비가 되었으니, 함께 기도제를 지낼 쿤쿤부족 주술사들을 깨워야한다고 말한다. 
777일동안의 기도를 지낸 후에, 777일 동안 깊은 잠에 
빠져 있는 쿤쿤부족 주술사들을 깨우자.
20001541-null-.manual: 천막에서 깊은 잠에 빠져 있는 쿤쿤부족 주술사 깨우기

20001541-null-NA.name: Wake-up Call
20001541-null-NA.desc: Now that $npcName:11000977$'s ritual is almost ready, it's time to awaken the kunkun shamans.

20001550-null-.name: QUESTDESCRIPTION_20001550_NAME
20001550-null-.desc:
$npc:11000744$ is a forest witch who used to brew a soup that has the power to grant any wish.
But after being tired of boiling soup all day, $npc:11000744$ started to daydream and began to imagine eating sweets, and somehow ended up in $map:02000185$.
$npc:11000744$ can't explain exactly what happened. The only thing she knows is that she needs to replenish her sugar as soon as possible! I have to follow the sweet scent to find something delicious for the forest witch!

20001560-null-.name: Back in Time
20001560-null-.desc:
$npc:11000984$ from the Andersen Village arrived in $map:02000185$ after messing up the incantation which resulted in the wrong door of time opening.
In order to open the door that leads to the town of fairy tales, $npc:11000984$ needs $item:30000301$, which was taken by $npc:21000278$.
It's time to hunt $npc:21000278$ and take the $item:30000301$ back.

20001561-null-.name: A Bold Move
20001561-null-.desc:
$npc:11000984$ is ready to go back to the Andersen Village, but $npc:11000984$'s friends morphed into violent monsters after warping through the distortion of time and space.
$npc:11000984$ feels responsible for this turn of events, and doesn't want to go back without fixing this.
For the safety of the Andersen Village and $map:02000185$, let's defeat $npc:21000278$, $npc:21000173$, and $npc:21000160$.

20001570-null-.name: 오리무중 연구
20001570-null-.desc:
$map:02000023$의 $npc:11000985$$pp:는,은$ 오랜 시간 인공지능 로봇에 대한 연구를 해왔다. 얼마 전 드디어 기나긴 연구의 끝을 알리는 인공지능 로봇 $npc:21000241$가 탄생하였지만, 결과는 그야말로 참담하기만 했다.
$map:02000023$$pp:를,을$ 정화시키고 관리할 목적으로 만들었던 $npc:21000241$가 숲을 파괴하고 있는 것이다.
프로그램이 어디서부터 오류를 냈는지 알 수는 없지만, 지금 당장은 $npc:21000241$ 파괴가 시급하다.
잘못 설계된 로봇 $npc:21000241$$pp:를,을$ 파괴시키자.

20001570-null-NA.name: Haywire
20001570-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000985$ has spent much of his career developing robots to help take care of the forests of $map:02000023$. However, his precious creations have gone haywire and are now laying waste to the very woods he sought to protect.

Now you must destroy the $npcPlural:21000241$ and figure out what went wrong.

20001571-null-.name: 포기란 없다
20001571-null-.desc:
$npc:11000985$$pp:는,은$ 평생을 바쳐 연구해온
$npc:21000241$$pp:를,을$ 이대로 포기할 수는 없다고 한다. 무슨 일이 있어도 잘못된 오류의 원인을 찾고, 모든걸 바로잡아 놓겠다는 $npc:11000985$.
당분간 연구소로 다시 복귀해 오류 데이터를 분석해야 하니, 임시 연구소에 설치해둔 중앙 처리 장치의 데이터를 복사해서 가져다 달라고 부탁한다. 
$map:02000128$에 있는 $npcName:11000985$ 연구실에서 $npc:11000985$$pp:가,이$ 건네준 $item:30000302$$pp:를,을$ 중앙 처리 장치에 넣어, 그동안의 모든 데이터를 복사해오자.

20001571-null-NA.name: Iteration
20001571-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000985$ refuses to give up just because his $npcPlural:21000241$ went berserk. He plans to carefully analyze the error that led to all this, but he needs the data from his computer if he's going to do so.

Go to his computer at the $map:02000128$ and copy the data onto the $item:30000302$ he gave you.
20001571-null-NA.manual: Copy the data from $npcName:11000985$'s lab at the $map:02000128$

20001580-null-.name: 잃어버린 탄생석
20001580-null-.desc:
$npc:11000986$$pp:는,은$ 하늘나라로 간 아빠가 물려준 자신의 보물 1호인 탄생 원석을 잃어버려 슬퍼하고 있다. 

힘들 때 힘이 되어준 친구들을 위해 탄생석을 세공하여 목걸이를 선물하려 했지만, 반짝이는 빛을 보고 근처의 몬스터들이 달려들어 빛나는 원석을 집어 삼켜 버렸다.

$map:02000128$에 서식하는 $npc:21000052$, $npc:21000004$으로부터 도난당한 $npc:11000986$의 소중한 탄생 원석을 되찾아오자.

20001580-null-NA.name: The Lost Stones
20001580-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11000986$ is upset that her birthstones—gifts left behind for her by her father—were stolen by monsters. She needs those gemstones to make a gift for her friends, who got her through some difficult times.

Reclaim the gemstones from the $npcPlural:21000052$ and $npcPlural:21000004$ living in $map:02000128$.

20001590-null-.name: 내 친구를 소개합니다
20001590-null-.desc:
잃어버린 탄생 원석을 찾은 $npc:11000986$$pp:는,은$ 감사의 뜻으로 자신에게 둘도 없는 은인이자 형제이기도 한 소중한 친구들을 소개해 주겠다고 한다.
그들은 엘리니아에서 잊혀진 보로보로 난쟁이들!
과연 보로보로들이 어떤 사연으로, 어디에서, 어떻게 살고 있는지 그들만의 세상으로 찾아가보자!
$map:02000128$ 꼭대기에 있는 $map:02000197$$pp:는,은$ 과연 어떤 곳일까?

20001590-null-NA.name: Secret Friends
20001590-null-NA.desc:
To thank you for retrieving her birthstones, $npc:11000986$ wants to introduce you to her very special friends. They're the boroboro, the forgotten fairfolk dwarves of Ellinia!

$map:02000197$ is at the top of the $map:02000128$. What kind of place could it be?
20001590-null-NA.manual: Enter $map:02000197$ through the top of the $map:02000128$

20001591-null-.name: 작지만 바쁜 시간
20001591-null-.desc:
$map:02000197$에서 만난 보로보로 할아버지 $npcName:11000987$. $npc:11000986$의 안부를 전해 듣자 경계심을 금방 푸는듯 하다. 
$npcName:11000987$$pp:는,은$ 아직은 말해줄 수 없는 보로보로 난쟁이들의 사연에 대해 잠시 고민을 하다가, 이내 중요한 시기에 평화롭게 낮잠이나 자고 있는 보로보로들이 문득 생각난다. 
$npcName:11000987$의 부탁대로, 낮잠을 자고 있는 보로보로들을 깨워보자.

20001591-null-NA.name: Moving Day
20001591-null-NA.desc: $npcName:11000987$, the boroboro elder in $map:02000197$, is upset that his fellow dwarves are being lazy bums during such a critical time. Help wake them up from their naps.
20001591-null-NA.manual: Wake up the boroboro dwarves in $map:02000197$

20001600-null-.name: 감시탑의 불청객
20001600-null-.desc:
$npc:11000959$$pp:는,은$ $map:02000091$을 홀로 지키며, 외로운 싸움을 하고 있다. 체력도 체력이지만 이제는 정신적으로도 많이 약해져버린 $npc:11000959$$pp:는,은$ 더 이상은 버틸 힘이 없다며 도움을 청해온다. 
$npc:11000959$$pp:를,을$ 도와 감시탑을 위협하고 있는 $npc:21000265$, $npc:21000306$$pp:를,을$ 소탕하자.

20001600-null-NA.name: The Lone Patrolman
20001600-null-NA.desc: $npc:11000959$ is guarding the $map:02000091$ alone. Pushed to his absolute limit, he can't hold the tower much longer without some help. Hold off the $npcNamePlural:21000265$ and $npcNamePlural:21000306$ while he fortifies his position.

20001601-null-.name: S.O.S
20001601-null-.desc:
다행히 감시탑 입구까지 몰려와 위협을 가하던 몬스터들의 수는 많이 줄어 들었다. 하지만 $npc:11000959$$pp:는,은$ 또 언제고 들이닥칠 수 있는 위협이기 때문에 이대로 마음을 놓고 있을 순 없다고 한다. 위협받고 있는 $map:02000091$을 지키기 위해 추가 병력 요청이 필요한 상황이다. 
$map:02000091$ 성벽에 있는 전서구를 날려 본부에  있는 대원들에게 지원을 요청하자.

20001601-null-NA.name: Call for Relief
20001601-null-NA.desc:
Fortunately, the majority of the monsters threatening the watchtower at the entrance have been defeated. Unfortunately, it's still too early to let your guard down because $npc:11000959$ can't hold off an attack on his own. The $map:02000091$ needs reinforcements.

Send a carrier pigeon from the $map:02000091$ to request reinforcements from headquarters.
20001601-null-NA.manual: Send a carrier pigeon to ask for reinforcements

20001610-null-.name: My Precious Chickens
20001610-null-.manual: Safely put the premium chickens grazing in the field to the poultry farm

20001620-null-.name: Sticky Situation
20001620-null-.desc:
From the corner of $map:02000196$ in $map:02000091$, a girl screams in horror. She says her name is $npc:11000960$, and the reason she let out such a bloodcurdling scream...is because toilet paper is nowhere to be found.
...It looks like she didn't check if there was any $item:30000313$ before taking care of business.
Let's show some sympathy and go through the emergency aid box to find $item:30000313$ for $npc:11000960$, who is in quite a sticky situation.
20001620-null-.manual: Go through the emergency aid box to find $item:30000313$

20001621-null-.name: First Contact
20001621-null-.desc:
You place the $item:30000313$ through the crack in the door, but $npc:11000960$ lets out another ear-piercing scream as soon as you turn around.
It turns out she can't reach the $item:30000313$ from where she is sitting...
At the end of her rope, $npc:11000960$ asks you to come in to the $map:02000196$... Could this situation get any worse...

20001622-null-.name: Battle for Bowels
20001622-null-.desc:
$npc:11000960$ confesses that she is currently suffering from...ahem...chronic constipation. She claims that consuming the $npc:21000353$ extract will relieve her from this painful condition.
Let's hunt $npc:21000353$ to relieve $npc:11000960$ from such a painful condition.

20001630-null-.name: 이미 엎질러진 물
20001630-null-.desc:
외모에 대한 콤플렉스를 가지고 있는 로로는 세계수 씨앗을 가지고 오면 외모를 바꿀 수 있는 묘약을 만들어 줄 수 있다는 $npc:11000746$의 농담을 진지하게 받아들인다. 혼자의 힘으로는 절대로 얻을 수 없는 세계수 씨앗을 갖기 위해, 숲속의 거인인 무무스에게 세뇌의 가면을 씌워 $map:02000103$$pp:를,을$ 쑥대밭으로 만들고 있는 로로.
점점 난폭해지는 $npc:23000035$$pp:를,을$ 제압하지 않으면 $map:02000023$의 심장부와도 같은 세계수 씨앗을 정말로 빼앗길지도 모른다. 
$npc:23000035$$pp:를,을$ 제압하고 무무스가 쓰고 있는 $item:30000329$$pp:를,을$ 가져오자.

20001630-null-NA.name: Undoing the Damage
20001630-null-NA.desc:
$npcName:11000746$ jokingly said that Lo could make himself more handsome if he had a seed from the $map:02000023$. She didn't expect him to actually try to take it! To make matters worse, he's placed an enchanted mask on Moomoo, turning the giant into his thrall.

Now it's up to you to take down $npc:23000035$ and get that $item:30000329$ back.

20001640-null-.name: 불길한 물방울
20001640-null-.desc:
숲의 요정 $npc:11000876$$pp:는,은$ 머리를 식히기 위해 빨간 점박이 무당벌레의 노래를 들으러 $map:02000215$에 갔다가 끔찍한 것을 보고야 말았다. 숲에 떠다니는 불길한 느낌의 보랏빛 물방울과, 더 끔찍한 것은 숲의 친구 빨간 점박이 무당벌레가 불길한 물방울에 오염되어 보랏빛으로 변해버린 것이다. 
$npc:11000876$$pp:는,은$ 이대로 가다가는 $map:02000215$ 전체가 병들어 버리고 말 거라며, 숲을 오염시키고 있는 도마구리를 처치해 달라고 한다.
$map:02000215$에서 $npc:21090176$, $npc:21090177$, $npc:21090175$$pp:를,을$ 사냥하자.

20001640-null-NA.name: Song of the Ladybugs
20001640-null-NA.desc:
$npcName:11000876$ went to $map:02000215$ to listen to the ladybugs sing, but it seems that something has made the ladybugs horribly sick. $npcName:11000876$ thinks that the $npcPlural:21090176$, $npcPlural:21090177$, and $npcPlural:21090175$ are behind this trouble.

You know what to do.

20001650-null-.name: 어느 별에서 왔니?
20001650-null-.desc:
동화 속 안데센 왕궁의 임금 $npcName:11001016$$pp:는,은$ 한 마법사에 의해 시간 여행을 떠나, 메이플 월드로 건너오게 되었다.
$map:02000181$에 도착한 $npcName:11001016$$pp:는,은$, 새로운 곳에서 자신만을 위한 왕궁을 세울 계획으로 곳곳을 둘러보던 중, 성 주변을 가득 메우고 있는 몬스터들을 발견한다. 왕궁을 꾸미는 것도 좋지만, 우선은 오랜 시간 성을 방치하면서 생겨난 몬스터들을 처치하는 것이 가장 시급할 것 같다는 $npcName:11001016$.
$map:02000181$ 주변을 어지럽히고 있는 $npc:21000220$, $npc:21000222$, $npc:21000266$$pp:를,을$ 처치하자.

20001650-null-NA.name: Another World
20001650-null-NA.desc: $npc:11001016$ was teleported through time and space to Maple World by a mage. With no way to get back to his own kingdom, he's decided to claim $map:02000181$ as his own. As the new liege in town, he's tasked you with clearing the castle grounds of $npcPlural:21000220$, $npcPlural:21000222$, and $npcPlural:21000266$.

20001660-null-.name: Rebellion of the Heretics
20001660-null-.desc:
$npc:11001053$ taught fighting skills to the Red Dragon Jaw Smashers, who were often ridiculed for their appearance. Unfortunately, the Red Dragon Jaw Smashers are abusing their skills to harass other innocent beings. Although $npc:11001053$ knows that's unacceptable, $npc:11001053$ still feels attached to the Red Dragon Jaw Smashers and would prefer having you do the job.
I suppose it's up to me to defeat $npc:21000312$, $npc:21000311$, and $npc:21000310$ occupying $map:02000093$.
20001660-null-.manual: Hunt the Red Dragon Jaw Smashers occupying $map:02000093$

20001670-null-.name: Innocence Lost
20001670-null-.desc:
$npc:11001052$ is trying to catch Little Croix, one of the Demon King's underlings. $npc:11001052$ rushed to $map:02000259$ after hearing that Croix was there, but it was too late... Croix was long gone after casting the spirit of the demon to the toys, thereby turning them into monsters.
$npc:11001052$ says that in order to find Little Croix, items that belong to the toy monsters imbued with the spirit of Croix are required.
I have to hunt $npc:21000279$, $npc:21000168$, and $npc:21000195$ in $map:02000259$, and acquire $item:30000359$, $item:30000360$, and $item:30000361$!
20001670-null-.manual: Hunt $npc:21000279$ to acquire $item:30000359$|Hunt $npc:21000168$ to acquire $item:30000360$|Hunt $npc:21000195$ to acquire $item:30000361$

20001680-null-.name: Money and Honor
20001680-null-.desc:
Some of the researchers from the $map:02000269$ ran away with the data containing an important technical document. $npc:11001033$ thinks they simply got tired of conducting the same research all day, and are planning to sell the technology to an unknown organization in $map:02000100$. But what $npc:11001033$ was most appalled by is the fact that they sprayed the sleeping gas that was developed to be equipped on weapons.
Fortunately, the effects of the weren't life-threatening to the researchers. Let's wake up the researchers who fell asleep because of the gas, and send them to a safe place.
20001680-null-.manual: Wake up the researchers who fell asleep because of the sleeping gas

20001690-null-.name: The Bunny and the Moon
20001690-null-.desc:
$npc:11000885$ was chasing the halo around the moon with friends in an attempt to travel through time, and somehow ended up in $map:02000280$.
$npcName:11000885$'s friends got hungry and ate some carrots they found on the field...but that turned them into monstrous bunnies. Who knew carrots could be so dangerous?
Let's defeat $npc:21090189$, $npc:21090187$, and $npc:21090188$, who all turned into monsters because of the curse.
20001690-null-.manual: Defeat the monster bunnies who became zombies due to the curse of time

20001710-null-.name: Isolated Agent
20001710-null-.desc: $npc:11001040$ from the marine exploratory base HQ got stuck in this place while investigating the mountain peak that suddenly froze when the dimensional rift of Ludibrium was twisted. $npc:11001040$ seems to be the only survivor in $map:02000260$, as all of the other researchers either disappeared in the snow, or lost their lives due to the monsters' attack. Let's defeat $npc:21000002$, $npc:21000199$, and $npc:21000089$, who are all blocking the way, so that $npcName:11001040$ can safely escape $map:02000260$.

20001720-null-.name: Mysterious Screams
20001720-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001041$ is looking pretty ragged. She says she's been kept up the last few nights by the echoes of children crying, madmen screaming, and animals howling. To make things work, prehistoric monsters have started showing up in the nearby fields.

$npcName:11001041$ is certain this is no coincidence, and wants you to bring her $itemPlural:30000345$, $itemPlural:30000346$, and $itemPlural:30000344$ to aid in her divinations.
20001720-null-.manual: Destroy icebergs to get $itemPlural:30000344$ |Hunt $npcNamePlural:21000199$ for $itemPlural:30000345$ |Hunt $npcNamePlural:21000089$ for $itemPlural:30000346$

20001721-null-.name: A Piercing Wind
20001721-null-.desc:
After her divination, $npcName:11001041$ is petrified with fear. She received visions of ancient $npcNamePlural:21000199$ and $npcNamePlural:21000089$ gathering to awaken $npcName:23000026$, an terrible demon who was defeated by the Sages. If the demon awakens, $map:02000260$ will surely be engulfed in icy darkness.

Defeat $npcName:23000026$ and avert this terrible prophecy.

20001750-null-.name: Christmas Clothes
20001750-null-.desc:
$npc:11001044$ delivers Christmas presents to children all over Maple World every year.
One day, $npc:11001044$ went to take a relaxing bath only to find out that monsters stole all of $item:30000348$ and $item:30000349$ upon his return.
Let's go to $map:02000261$ to reclaim Papa Santa's items that were stolen by $npc:21000227$ and $npc:21000263$.
20001750-null-.manual: Go to $map:02000261$ to reclaim $item:30000348$ from the monsters|Go to $map:02000261$ to reclaim $item:30000349$ from the monsters

20001760-null-.name: Shocking Development
20001760-null-.desc:
$npc:11001045$ was dispatched to fix the utility pole that was letting out sparks in $map:02000276$.
$npc:11001045$ found out that the electric current is much stronger than expected, and is worried about not being able to check all of the utility poles before all of the electricity leaks out.
I'll have to find the high-voltage electrical wire and disconnect it to help $npc:11001045$.

20001770-null-.name: Research Gone Wrong
20001770-null-.desc:
A long time ago, Dr. Kernel discovered that magnetic energy and electricity are combined, immense power can be drawn out. Wanting to find out just how powerful this energy can be, Dr. Kernel performed an experiment that was considered extremely controversial on a wild bear. But this experiment went awry, and $npc:22000023$ the electrical bear was created. No one was able to control this vicious bear, and it not only injured Dr. Kernel, but also destroyed the entirety of $map:02000276$.
I must defeat $npc:22000023$ that is putting $map:02000276$ in great peril.

20001780-null-.name: Listen to Me...Or Else
20001780-null-.desc: $npc:11001047$ is not very happy about how the reformation project of the Goldus Industrial Development Institute is going. Despite its objective of trying to provide jobs for criminals and hoodlums instead of sending them to jail, these ungrateful delinquents don't care about  jobs and are slacking off all day. $npc:11001047$ request that I teach them a lesson so that they can get back to work.

20001790-null-.name: Shrouded in Darkness
20001790-null-.desc: As most unicorns have disappeared after getting possessed by demonic spirits, only a handful of unicorns remain. They've been hiding in $map:02000192$ as they attempt to recover their magical power. Despite their efforts, they've been getting weaker ever since the Kwinko Grave Robbers have begun occupying $map:02000192$. A unicorn named $npc:11001058$ is asking if you can get the $item:30000352$ back, as the unicorns cannot regain their power without it. I'll have to defeat $npc:21091023$, $npc:21000110$, and $npc:21091021$ to reclaim the $item:30000352$.
20001790-null-.manual: Reclaim the stolen $item:30000352$ from the monsters in $map:02000192$

20001791-null-.name: This Little Light of Mine
20001791-null-.desc:
Now that $npc:11001058$ has the $item:30000352$, there's one last thing to do before the unicorns can regain their lost power. $npc:11001058$ says if I light up the extinguished beacon crystal, they will then be able to receive the regenerative energy from the crystal.
Let's light up the extinguished beacon crystal in $map:02000192$.
20001791-null-.manual: Light up the extinguished beacon crystal in $map:02000192$

20001800-null-.name: Everlasting Childhood
20001800-null-.desc:
Living in the space of suspended time, $npc:11000783$ is unbelievably bored, as every day feels the same. $npc:11000783$ now understands why his girlfriend Korin left this place to become an adult. $npc:11000783$ asked you if you could help him get $item:30000378$, so that he too can become an adult... and maybe find Korin one day as well.
Let's hunt $npc:21000163$, $npc:21000171$, and $npc:21000194$ in $map:02000262$ to acquire $item:30000378$.

20001810-null-.name: Enemy or Ally
20001810-null-.manual: Bring $item:30000353$ that is being kept in the energy storage capsule

20001820-null-.name: Beloved Brother
20001820-null-.desc: $npc:11001076$ is part of the Snowfolk, and is the younger brother of $npcName:11000018$, the weapon seller in $map:02000051$. To meet his brother, he decided to leave his hometown and venture into $map:02000051$. On his way to $map:02000051$, $npc:11001076$ heard about $item:30000351$, a highly valuable and expensive material for a weapon. It can be found in $map:02000011$, but Snowfolk like $npc:11001076$ won't be able to endure the hot temperature. I'll have to acquire $item:30000351$ for $npc:11001076$.
20001820-null-.manual: Find the red rock in $map:02000011$ and acquire $item:30000351$

20001830-null-.name: Typical Masterminds
20001830-null-.desc: $npc:11000837$ noticed the greedy Kwinko Grave Robbers were acting suspicious, and decided to track them. The Kwinko Grave Robbers arrived in $map:02000176$, which is one of the ancient ruins managed by the Ereve Royal Court. $npc:11000837$ is determined to reveal all of their schemes once and for all. $npc:11000837$ request that I defeat $npc:21091022$, $npc:21091024$, and $npc:21091094$, to stop them from stealing the relics while $npc:11000837$ goes for the leader of the Kwinko Grave Robbers.
20001830-null-.manual: Defeat the monsters trying to steal relics in $map:02000176$

20001850-null-.name: Believe It or Not
20001850-null-.desc:
Getting tired of going through the same routine every day, $npc:11001059$ went fishing to relieve some stress. $npc:11001059$ dozed off while fishing, however, and somehow woke up in $map:02000263$. But because $npc:11001059$ enjoys ice fishing so much, $npc:11001059$ isn't questioning how it happened, or isn't even trying to get back home.
...Despite that, $npc:11001059$ asked me to kick out $npc:21091024$ and $npc:21091022$ disturbing the otherwise peaceful and quiet fishing grounds.

20001851-null-.name: Midlife Crisis
20001851-null-.desc: $npc:11001059$ is really getting into ice fishing! But $npc:11001059$ still isn't used to the cold weather in $map:02000263$. It's plainly obvious it's going to take a while to catch some big fish. $npc:11001059$ is asking if I could help him make a fire around the fishing area. $npc:11001059$ also needs $item:30000358$, which could be used as bait.
20001851-null-.manual: Acquire $item:30000354$ to make a fire|Catch $item:30000358$ to be used as fishing bait

20001860-null-.name: Plotting Schemes
20001860-null-.desc:
Arguing that the archaic research methods and just plain stubbornness are getting in the way of technological development, $npc:11000848$ wants to release the technology containing all the crucial information collected over the years...in exchange for obscene amounts of money. $npc:11000848$ wants me to collect the core energy sources that have been planted inside the monsters in the center.
Let's defeat $npc:21000296$, $npc:21000248$, and $npc:21000110$ in $map:02000274$, and collect $item:30000355$ and $item:30000356$.
20001860-null-.manual: Hunt monsters in $map:02000274$ to collect $item:30000355$|Hunt monsters in $map:02000274$ to collect $item:30000356$

20001880-null-.name: (Dungeon) Piece of Cake
20001880-null-.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20014002$ 
(Entrance: $map:02000011$)
Party Size: 10
The quest is only available in challenge mode.

By imperial decree, any prisoner who defeats $npcName:23100011$ 50 or more times in $map:02000311$ will be granted a special pardon. $npcName:11001079$ wants to take advantage of this opportunity, but he's getting cold feat about facing $npcName:23100011$. Perhaps you can go in his place.

20001880-null-NA.name: Dungeon: Piece of Cake
20001880-null-NA.desc:
$dungeonTitle:20014002$ 
(Entrance: $map:02000011$)
Party Size: 10
The quest is only available in challenge mode.

By imperial decree, any prisoner who defeats $npcName:23100011$ 50 or more times in $map:02000311$ will be granted a special pardon. $npcName:11001079$ wants to take advantage of this opportunity, but he's getting cold feet about facing $npcName:23100011$. Perhaps you can go in his place.

20001910-null-.name: 위험에 노출된 환경
20001910-null-.desc:
$npc:11001140$$pp:는,은$ $map:02000110$ 곳곳에 방치되어 있는 가스통이 주변의 $npc:21000281$$pp:가,이$ 던지는 폭탄 때문에 폭발할 위험성이 크다고 한다. 
가스통을 점검하고, 가스가 새지 않도록 단단히 밸브를 잠그자.

20001910-null-NA.name: Hazardous Working Conditions
20001910-null-NA.desc:
$npc:11001140$ says the gas tanks around $map:02000110$ are dangerous. If one of the $npc:21000281$ throws a bomb the wrong direction, they're all doomed.
$npc:11001140$ needs you to lend a hand inspecting the gas tanks for leaks and making sure all the valves are closed, so they don't have a major accident.
20001910-null-NA.manual: Inspect the gas tanks to prevent an explosion in $map:02000110$

20001990-null-.name: The Green Menace
20001990-null-.desc: $npcName:11001328$ has a grudge against the turtles of $map:02010043$ ever since they spooked his salamander mount. He's asked you to do something about the $npcNamePlural:21000143$, $npcNamePlural:21000144$, and $npcNamePlural:21000145$ so that they never terrorize a poor, defenseless salamander ever again.

20002000-null-.name: A Daring Theft
20002000-null-.desc:
Last night, a gang of $npcNamePlural:21000423$ and $npcNamePlural:21000417$ busted into $npcName:11001350$'s vacation home and stole a bunch of $itemPlural:30000451$.

$npcName:11001329$, who is supposed to be watching the home, is in a panic. See if you can help reclaim the stolen goods.
20002000-null-.manual: Reclaim $itemPlural:30000451$ stolen by the monsters in $map:02010084$

20002010-null-.name: Mr. Arthur's Day Out
20002010-null-.desc: $npcName:11001330$ is drowning his sorrows in cheeseburgers, but no amount of ground beef can solve his marital troubles. Find out if there's any way you can help.

20002011-null-.name: Mrs. Arthur's Day Out
20002011-null-.desc: After a hard day's shopping, $npcName:11001331$ was rewarded by having all of her new items stolen by monsters! She refuses to go home until she gets everything back. Hunt the $npcNamePlural:21000726$, $npcNamePlural:21000720$, and $npcNamePlural:21000714$ around $map:02010010$ and retrieve her $itemPlural:30000452$.

20002020-null-.name: A Mall in Crisis
20002020-null-.desc: $npcName:11001332$, president of the $map:02010010$ Merchant Union, is overwhelmed by customer complaints. It seems that rampaging monsters are bad for business. Defeat the $npcNamePlural:21000726$, $npcNamePlural:21000720$, and $npcNamePlural:21000714$ that have attacked $map:02010010$.

20002030-null-.name: Addicted to Coconade
20002030-null-.desc: $npcName:11001333$'s pet $npcName:11001334$ is throwing a tantrum because he wants to drink $item:30000453$. You know just how to handle a tantrum: give him whatever he wants until he shuts up.
20002030-null-.manual: Get $item:30000453$ from the vending machine in $map:02010010$

20002040-null-.name: Laziness Is a Virtue
20002040-null-.desc: $npcName:11001335$ wants to return the skateboard he rented, but the shop is just too far, see? Now that it's past due, he's looking for someone to return it to $npcName:11001336$. Are you that someone?

20002041-null-.name: Late Fees
20002041-null-.desc: $npcName:11001336$ asked you to collect the abandoned rental skateboards scattered around $map:02010014$.

20002050-null-.name: The Thieving Swarm
20002050-null-.desc: $npcName:11001336$ is in utter shock after a swarm of bugs stole all of his $itemPlural:30000458$. Find the $npcNamePlural:21000434$ and $npcNamePlural:21000438$ in $map:02010014$ and get the stolen goods back.

20002060-null-.name: Bugging Out
20002060-null-.desc: $npcName:11001340$ in $map:02010014$ is having insect troubles at his food truck. Get rid of the $npcNamePlural:21000434$ and $npcNamePlural:21000438$ swarming the area.
20002060-null-.manual: Get rid of the bugs attacking $map:02010014$

20002070-null-.name: A Call for Help
20002070-null-.desc: $npcName:11001341$ was dispatched to $map:02010014$ to make war on the bugs there, but he was quickly overwhelmed. Find $npcName:11001342$ in $map:02010019$ and ask for backup.

20002081-null-.name: Like Rats in a Trap
20002081-null-.desc: $npcName:11001344$ has come to $map:02010019$ in search of escapees from Alikar Prison. With his keen guarding skills and your ability to look under beds and in closets, you'll recapture the inmates in no time.

20002090-null-.name: Impostors
20002090-null-.desc: $npcName:11001370$ claims that monsters have disguised themselves as repairmen and broken into $map:02010009$. Defeat the $npcNamePlural:21000735$ and $npcNamePlural:21000732$.

20002091-null-.name: Safety First
20002091-null-.desc: $npcName:11001370$ is worried about the real repairmen who were trapped in $map:52010009$. Help get them to safety.

20002100-null-.name: Precious Gifts
20002100-null-.desc: $npcName:11001373$ is on the verge of tears because all the gifts she bought for her family were stolen by monsters during the evacuation. Hunt down $npcNamePlural:21000735$ and $npcNamePlural:21000732$ in $map:02010009$ to get the $itemPlural:30000479$ back.

20002140-null-.name: Quality Television
20002140-null-.desc: Reality television! That's the future! $npcName:11001376$ is going to hit the big time with real live footage of the chaos at $map:02010020$. Gather the $itemPlural:30000482$ for him.

20002150-null-.name: Fair and Square
20002150-null-.desc: $npcName:11001377$ is suspicious of the results of the latest match. Collect the $item:30000483$ from $map:52010010$ to help assuage—or confirm—her fears.

30000012-null-.name: The New World
30000012-null-.desc: Apparently, $npc:11000019$ is a huge fan of $npc:11000444$. Let's take $item:30000151$ to $npcName:11000444$, and let $npcName:11000444$ know that $item:30000151$ can be taken from $npc:11000019$'s drawer at $npc:11000019$ anytime.

30000020-null-.name: The Forgotten Incident
30000020-null-.desc:
After taking out a scrapbook consisting of articles relating to Dr. Kartronic, $map:02000145$'s $npc:11000372$ asked me to help $npc:11001032$, who is currently investigating Dr. Kartronic's most recent project...the MK Project.
Is $npc:23000054$ really related to the MK Project?

30000021-null-.name: Private Project
30000021-null-.desc: While looking over $item:39000005$, $map:02000187$'s $npc:11001032$ tried his best to remember every single detail. Wondering where the necessary clues could be found, he said that looking over the robots in $map:02000187$ might help in finding $item:39000006$. Let's go look at the robots as he suggested.

30000022-null-.name: Doctor's Den
30000022-null-.desc:
After closely examining $item:39000006$, $map:02000187$'s $npc:11001032$ was certain that $map:02000232$ will help figure out why the MK Project failed.
But in order to enter, more information is still needed. $npc:11001032$ asked me to investigate the computers in $map:02000187$ and bring $item:30000357$.

30000030-null-.name: Valuable Rubble
30000030-null-.desc: $npc:11000135$ at $map:02000044$ heard that the rare $item:30000055$ can be found at $map:02000235$. $npc:11000135$ also said that it's a pretty expensive and valuable item, and asked me to acquire some.

30000031-null-.name: Ancient Relic
30000031-null-.desc: After finding $item:30000056$ mixed inside $item:30000055$, $npc:11000135$ began violently trembling in fear. When I asked him what was wrong, all $npc:11000135$ told me was to take it to $npc:11000039$.

30000032-null-.name: In Search of Vayar
30000032-null-.desc:
$npc:11000039$ said that $item:30000056$ can be used to locate the Stone Giants spread out across the world. However, $npc:23100006$, the strongest (and most evil) one of them all, cannot be tracked down accurately.
Sharper than a blade, and colder than the harshest winter!
The salty scent of the ocean, penetrating both the nostrils and lungs!
Let's carefully consider these clues from $npc:11000039$, and look for any traces of $npc:23100006$.

30000040-null-.name: Foretold
30000040-null-.desc:
You spoke with $npc:11000144$ at $map:02000173$ who asked you to help him repay his life-debt by preventing $npc:23090005$'s reawakening. $npcName:11000144$'s willingness to put his life on the line to keep his promise is inspiring

You should help $npc:11000144$ defeat the monsters of $map:02000268$ and locate$item:30000157$ to defy what was prophesied. Once you have found it, bring it to $npc:11001046$ at $map:02000268$ to learn how to stop the $npc:23090005$.
30000040-null-.manual: Defeat the monsters in $map:02000268$ and find the $item:30000157$

30000041-null-.name: The Blade of a Hero
30000041-null-.desc:
After transforming the $item:30000157$ back into the $item:13200028$ and packing it in the $item:30000155$, $npcName:11001046$ asked you to deliver it to $npcName:11000144$.

He also had another request: for you to tell $npcName:11000144$ that $item:13200028$ can be restored to its true power by. All he needs to do is find the $item:30000153$ below the stone grave markers where the nameless heroes rest, then to use the Cleansing Flames to transform it into the $item:30000154$, and place within the $item:13200028$.

You should hurry over to $map:02000173$ and let $npc:11000144$ know before you forget.

30000042-null-.name: The $item:30000153$
30000042-null-.desc:
Find the $item:30000153$, which contains the souls of the heroes who sealed away the $npc:23090005$ within $map:02000200$.

Once you've done that, cast it into the $npc:11000345$.
30000042-null-.manual: Search the stone grave markers in $map:02000200$ and locate the $item:30000153$

30000043-null-.name: Wake the Dead
30000043-null-.desc:
Onward to the $map:02000200$! You must cast the $item:30000153$ into the $npc:11000345$ at the end of the path!

If what you've been told is true, that will awaken the soul within the $item:30000153$ and cause it to transform into the $item:30000154$.

Once you have obtained the $item:30000154$ take it to $npc:11000144$ and instruct him to embed it within the $item:13200028$.

30000050-null-.name: Mechanical Monsters: An Illustrated Guide
30000050-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001179$ is developing a line of illustrated monster guides to sell for his business. To incentivize your assistance gathering data, he has offered you not only a substantial reward, but credit as a co-author. 

You agreed to analyze the battle tactics and capabilities of machine monsters. As there are said to be a large number in $map:2000270$, that seems like an excellent place to begin your research.
30000050-null-.manual: Battle Machine monsters to learn more about them

30000051-null-.name: Invasive Insectoids: An Illustrated Guide
30000051-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001179$ is developing a line of illustrated monster guides to sell for his business. To incentivize your assistance gathering data, he has offered you not only a substantial reward, but credit as a co-author. 

Although insect monsters are found all across the world, it's said that there is an especially high number of them in the areas around  $map:2000023$. That should be a good place to start your research.
30000051-null-.manual: Battle insect monsters to learn more about them

30000052-null-.name: Inanimate Monsters: An Illustrated Guide
30000052-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001179$ is developing a line of illustrated monster guides to sell for his business. To incentivize your assistance gathering data, he has offered you not only a substantial reward, but credit as a co-author. 

Although inanimate monsters can be found around the world, they are said to be plentiful around areas that have been transformed into Ludibrium blocks. You should search such locations for monsters to battle and analyze.
30000052-null-.manual: Battle inanimate monsters to learn more about them

30000053-null-.name: Perilous Plants: An Illustrated Guide
30000053-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001179$ is developing a line of illustrated monster guides to sell for his business. To incentivize your assistance gathering data, he has offered you not only a substantial reward, but credit as a co-author. 

Seeing as plant monsters can be found nearly anywhere, you can challenge them wherever you like, and study their tactics.
30000053-null-.manual: Battle plant monsters to learn more about them

30000054-null-.name: Divine Beasts: An Illustrated Guide
30000054-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001179$ is developing a line of illustrated monster guides to sell for his business. To incentivize your assistance gathering data, he has offered you not only a substantial reward, but credit as a co-author. 

Divine monsters may be rare, but you don't give up easy. Locate and defeat divine monsters, and share what you learn in the process!
30000054-null-.manual: Battle divine monsters to learn more about them

30000055-null-.name: Devilish Dangers: An Illustrated Guide
30000055-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001179$ is developing a line of illustrated monster guides to sell for his business. To incentivize your assistance gathering data, he has offered you not only a substantial reward, but credit as a co-author. 

Devil monsters are usually found in the Land of Darkness, but they can also be found in other parts of Maple World touched by shadow. Defeat devil monsters and record your findings!
30000055-null-.manual: Battle devil monsters to learn more about them

30000056-null-.name: Barbarous Beasts: An Illustrated Guide
30000056-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001179$ is developing a line of illustrated monster guides to sell for his business. To incentivize your assistance gathering data, he has offered you not only a substantial reward, but credit as a co-author. 

Considering how beast monsters can be found nearly anywhere, you can challenge them wherever you like, and study their tactics.
30000056-null-.manual: Battle beast monsters to learn more about them

30000057-null-.name: Understanding the Undead: An Illustrated Guide
30000057-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001179$ is developing a line of illustrated monster guides to sell for his business. To incentivize your assistance gathering data, he has offered you not only a substantial reward, but credit as a co-author. 

Undead monsters are known to dwell in dark places like the Ant Tunnel or the Land of Darkness. Those places seem as good as any to start your monster research.
30000057-null-.manual: Battle undead monsters to learn more about them

30000058-null-.name: Fiendish Fairies: An Illustrated Guide
30000058-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001179$ is developing a line of illustrated monster guides to sell for his business. To incentivize your assistance gathering data, he has offered you not only a substantial reward, but credit as a co-author. 

It's said that fairy monsters can be found in the areas surrounding $map:2000076$ and $map:2000023$. You should pick one and begin your monster research.
30000058-null-.manual: Battle fairy monsters to learn more about them

30000059-null-.name: Horrible Humanoids: An Illustrated Guide
30000059-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001179$ is developing a line of illustrated monster guides to sell for his business. To incentivize your assistance gathering data, he has offered you not only a substantial reward, but credit as a co-author. 

It's said that humanoid foes can be found in the areas around $map:2000100$. You should start your investigative hunt there!
30000059-null-.manual: Battle humanoid foes to learn more about them

30000060-null-.name: Spiteful Spirits: An Illustrated Guide
30000060-null-.desc:
$npcName:11001179$ is developing a line of illustrated monster guides to sell for his business. To incentivize your assistance gathering data, he has offered you not only a substantial reward, but credit as a co-author. 

Spirit monsters can be found all over the place. Find some to battle, and document your findings!
30000060-null-.manual: Battle spirit monsters to learn more about them

30000100-null-.name: Barrels of Fun
30000100-null-.desc:
$npc:11001179$ wants you to investigate if Flaming Barrels can be effectively used as weapons. You should be able to find some in the areas surrounding $map:2000270$.

Go find out how useful they are by throwing them at enemies!

30000101-null-.name: Cartloads of Chaos
30000101-null-.desc:
$npc:11001179$ wants you to investigate whether mine carts can be effectively used as weapons. Mine carts can be found near the Ant Tunnels or inside abandoned mines.

Go find out how useful they are by throwing them at enemies!
30000101-null-.manual: Attack enemies with rolling mine carts

30000102-null-.name: Booming Barrels
30000102-null-.desc:
$npc:11001179$ wants you to investigate whether explosives barrels can be effectively used as weapons. Explosives barrels can be found within the Ant Tunnels or near pirate-infested beaches.

Go find out how useful they are by using them on enemies!

30000103-null-.name: Terrible Tires
30000103-null-.desc:

30000200-null-.name: Notorious Monsters: Fragmented Soul
30000200-null-.desc:
Overwhelmed with the monumental task of documenting every monster in Maple World in a single compendium, $npcName:11001179$ has decided to publish a small digest containing only the most notorious and powerful adversaries.

Having heard from a traveler about the powerful entity known as $npc:22000045$, $npcName:11001179$ has tasked you with identifying your new target's strengths and weaknesses. With your aid, this booklet is bound to be a best-seller! Defeat $npc:22000045$ at $map:02000262$, and report back with everything you learn!
